WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

2
00:00:17.851 --> 00:00:19.853
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

3
00:02:45.082 --> 00:02:46.675
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

4
00:02:56.510 --> 00:02:58.854
This will begin to make things right.

5
00:02:59.763 --> 00:03:02.767
I've traveled too far and seen too much

6
00:03:02.849 --> 00:03:05.819
to ignore the despair in the galaxy.

7
00:03:05.936 --> 00:03:09.782
Without the Jedi. there can be
no balance in the Force.

8
00:03:10.607 --> 00:03:13.156
Well. because of you.
now we have a chance.

9
00:03:13.276 --> 00:03:15.028
The General's been after this
for a long time.

10
00:03:15.487 --> 00:03:16.909
Oh. the General?

11
00:03:16.988 --> 00:03:19.366
To me. she is royalty.

12
00:03:19.783 --> 00:03:21.376
Well. she certainly is that.

13
00:03:21.451 --> 00:03:23.795
-(SLATS CLATTERING)
-(BB-8 CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

14
00:03:27.207 --> 00:03:28.379
We got company.

15
00:03:28.834 --> 00:03:30.586
(VILLAGERS SHOUTING
INDISTINCTLY)

16
00:03:33.213 --> 00:03:34.430
(SHOUTING CONTINUES)

17
00:03:41.430 --> 00:03:42.977
You have to hide.

18
00:03:43.098 --> 00:03:44.520
You have to leave.

19
00:03:46.643 --> 00:03:47.644
Go.

20
00:03:47.811 --> 00:03:49.484
-(VILLAGERS CLAMORING)
-(BELL TOLLING)

21
00:03:52.983 --> 00:03:55.202
-(VILLAGER SCREAMS)
-(CLAMORING CONTINUES)

22
00:03:58.196 --> 00:03:59.539
(BLASTER COCKING)

23
00:04:05.954 --> 00:04:07.706
(INDISTINCT SCREAMING
AND SHOUTING)

24
00:04:07.831 --> 00:04:09.833
(INDISTINCT STORMTROOPER
RADIO CHATTER)

25
00:04:17.549 --> 00:04:18.892
(POE PANTING)

26
00:04:19.009 --> 00:04:21.353
- Come on. BB-8. hurry!
-(BB-8 CHIRPS)

27
00:04:27.184 --> 00:04:28.857
-(ENGINES REVVING)
-(BB-8 CHIRPS NERVOUSLY)

28
00:04:32.355 --> 00:04:33.481
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

29
00:04:33.607 --> 00:04:34.733
<i>STORMTROOPER'. Blast that X-Wing!</i>

30
00:04:34.816 --> 00:04:35.988
<i>Over there! Over there!</i>

31
00:04:36.443 --> 00:04:37.990
-(POE GROANS)
-(ALARMS RINGING)

32
00:04:41.031 --> 00:04:43.125
-(BB-8 CHIRPING)
- I see them.

33
00:04:57.047 --> 00:04:58.720
(VILLAGER CHITTERING
NERVOUSLY)

34
00:05:14.731 --> 00:05:15.698
You take this.

35
00:05:15.774 --> 00:05:17.742
It's safer with you than it is with me.

36
00:05:18.568 --> 00:05:20.696
You get as far away from here
as you can.

37
00:05:21.863 --> 00:05:23.581
- Do you hear me?
-(BB-8 CHIRPS)

38
00:05:23.698 --> 00:05:25.075
I'll come back for you.

39
00:05:25.742 --> 00:05:27.119
Itwill be all right.

40
00:05:30.247 --> 00:05:31.248
(BLASTER COCKING)

41
00:05:36.711 --> 00:05:37.963
(STORMTROOPER GROANS)

42
00:05:57.858 --> 00:05:59.235
(FN-2187 GASPING)

43
00:06:26.177 --> 00:06:27.474
STORMTROOPER 1: Keep moving!

44
00:06:29.639 --> 00:06:30.982
STORMTROOPER 2: Stay here.

45
00:06:54.372 --> 00:06:57.251
<i>KYLO REN:
Look how old you've become.</i>

46
00:06:57.918 --> 00:07:00.888
Something far worse
has happened to you.

47
00:07:01.671 --> 00:07:03.673
<i>You know what I've come for.</i>

48
00:07:04.049 --> 00:07:05.972
I know where you come from.

49
00:07:06.051 --> 00:07:08.019
Before you called yourself Kylo Ren.

50
00:07:08.511 --> 00:07:12.106
<i>The map to Skywalker.
We know you found it.</i>

51
00:07:13.266 --> 00:07:16.019
<i>And now you're going
to give it to the First Order.</i>

52
00:07:16.144 --> 00:07:18.613
The First Order rose from the dark side.

53
00:07:18.688 --> 00:07:19.689
You did not.

54
00:07:20.857 --> 00:07:23.360
<i>I'll show you the dark side.</i>

55
00:07:24.027 --> 00:07:25.700
You may try.

56
00:07:25.779 --> 00:07:29.784
But you cannot deny
the truth that is your family.

57
00:07:30.533 --> 00:07:31.580
<i>You're so right.</i>

58
00:07:31.660 --> 00:07:32.957
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

59
00:07:39.334 --> 00:07:40.881
(BLASTER BOLT CRACKLING)

60
00:07:42.379 --> 00:07:43.505
(POE GROANS)

61
00:07:47.258 --> 00:07:48.885
(BOLT PULSATING)

62
00:07:53.473 --> 00:07:54.725
(GROANS)

63
00:08:05.610 --> 00:08:07.908
So. who talks first?
You talk first? I talk first?

64
00:08:09.072 --> 00:08:10.949
<i>KYLO REN: The old man gave it to you.</i>

65
00:08:11.116 --> 00:08:12.709
It's just very hard to
understand you with all the...

66
00:08:12.784 --> 00:08:14.411
- Search him.
-...apparatus.

67
00:08:18.456 --> 00:08:20.333
<i>STORMTROOPER: Nothing. sir.
KYLO REN: Put him on board.</i>

68
00:08:26.464 --> 00:08:28.967
<i>PHASMA". Sir. the villagers?</i>

69
00:08:31.553 --> 00:08:32.770
<i>- Kill them all.
-(BLASTERS COCKING)</i>

70
00:08:32.971 --> 00:08:34.097
(VILLAGERS EXCLAIMING)

71
00:08:34.264 --> 00:08:35.857
<i>PHASMA: On my command.</i>

72
00:08:36.808 --> 00:08:38.185
<i>Fire.</i>

73
00:08:38.268 --> 00:08:40.270
-(VILLAGERS SCREAMING)
- POE: Please. no!

74
00:08:49.654 --> 00:08:51.497
(INDISTINCT STORMTROOPER
RADIO CHATTER)

75
00:09:01.624 --> 00:09:02.967
(BOLT CRACKLING)

76
00:09:05.211 --> 00:09:06.588
(FN-2187 GASPS)

77
00:09:08.757 --> 00:09:10.555
STORMTROOPER: Nothing here.
Go ahead!

78
00:09:14.137 --> 00:09:15.514
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

79
00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:22.153
(BB-8 MOANS SOFTLY)

80
00:09:30.612 --> 00:09:32.159
(CREATURE EXCLAIMS
IN ALIEN DIALECT)

81
00:09:51.591 --> 00:09:52.683
All right.

82
00:09:52.759 --> 00:09:53.760
All right!

83
00:09:55.095 --> 00:09:57.018
(INDISTINCT PA CHATTER)

84
00:10:03.645 --> 00:10:05.192
(FN-2187 PANTING)

85
00:10:12.987 --> 00:10:14.489
(GASPING)

86
00:10:19.661 --> 00:10:21.379
<i>PHASMA'. FN-2187.</i>

87
00:10:22.038 --> 00:10:24.541
<i>Submit your blaster for inspection.</i>

88
00:10:25.208 --> 00:10:26.460
Yes. Captain.

89
00:10:27.001 --> 00:10:29.720
<i>And who gave you permission
to remove that helmet?</i>

90
00:10:30.380 --> 00:10:31.381
I'm sorry. Captain.

91
00:10:31.464 --> 00:10:33.558
<i>Report to my division at once.</i>

92
00:11:22.599 --> 00:11:24.442
(PANTING)

93
00:12:15.818 --> 00:12:17.070
(SPEEDER REVVING)

94
00:12:47.141 --> 00:12:48.734
(REY SIGHS)

95
00:13:12.333 --> 00:13:13.459
-(STAFF CLACKS)
-(SCAVENGER 1 EXCLAIMS)

96
00:13:13.543 --> 00:13:14.920
(CHITTERING IN ALIEN DIALECT)

97
00:13:15.003 --> 00:13:16.755
(SCAVENGER <i>2</i> LAUGHING)

98
00:13:19.257 --> 00:13:22.511
UNKAR: What you brought
me today is worth...

99
00:13:22.635 --> 00:13:24.308
hmm...

100
00:13:25.555 --> 00:13:28.354
one quarter portion.

101
00:13:40.987 --> 00:13:43.081
(SPEEDER RACING)

102
00:14:11.267 --> 00:14:12.519
(SIZZLING)

103
00:14:23.363 --> 00:14:24.455
(FAINT BOOMING)

104
00:14:48.971 --> 00:14:51.440
(BB-8 CHIRPING FAINTLY)

105
00:14:54.352 --> 00:14:56.025
(BB-8 CHIRPING NERVOUSLY)

106
00:14:56.104 --> 00:14:58.323
(TEEDO SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

107
00:15:01.692 --> 00:15:03.615
-(TEEDO EXCLAIMING)
-(BB-8 CHIRPING)

108
00:15:04.529 --> 00:15:06.247
(TEEDO SHOUTING
IN ALIEN DIALECT)

109
00:15:06.823 --> 00:15:07.995
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

110
00:15:08.116 --> 00:15:09.493
(TEEDO AND BB-8 EXCLAIMING)

111
00:15:09.659 --> 00:15:11.002
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

112
00:15:12.495 --> 00:15:14.168
(REY SHOUTING IN ALIEN DIALECT)

113
00:15:16.290 --> 00:15:17.667
-(TEEDO CHITTERING)
-(BB-8 CHIRPING)

114
00:15:17.834 --> 00:15:20.633
(TEEDO AND REY ARGUING
IN ALIEN DIALECT)

115
00:15:23.339 --> 00:15:25.512
(TEEDO SCOFFS)

116
00:15:25.633 --> 00:15:28.011
-(BB-8 CHIRPS ANGRILY)
- Shh.

117
00:15:30.054 --> 00:15:32.352
That's just Teedo. Wants you for parts.

118
00:15:33.057 --> 00:15:34.650
He has no respect for anyone.

119
00:15:35.017 --> 00:15:36.018
(BB-8 EXCLAIMS SOFTLY)

120
00:15:38.354 --> 00:15:39.446
Your antenna's bent.

121
00:15:49.198 --> 00:15:50.245
Where do you come from?

122
00:15:50.408 --> 00:15:51.705
(BB-8 CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

123
00:15:54.036 --> 00:15:55.834
- Classified. really?
-(CHIRPS MERRILY)

124
00:15:55.913 --> 00:15:57.210
Me too. Big secret.

125
00:15:58.124 --> 00:16:01.219
Niima Outpost is that way.
Stay off Kelvin Ridge.

126
00:16:01.377 --> 00:16:03.175
Keep away from
the Sinking Fields in the north.

127
00:16:03.337 --> 00:16:04.759
You'll drown in the sand.

128
00:16:05.631 --> 00:16:08.475
(BB-8 CHIRPING HAPPILY)

129
00:16:10.094 --> 00:16:12.973
Don't follow me. Town is that way.

130
00:16:13.097 --> 00:16:14.144
(BB-8 SIGHS)

131
00:16:14.849 --> 00:16:16.101
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

132
00:16:16.184 --> 00:16:17.185
No!

133
00:16:18.269 --> 00:16:20.112
(BB-8 MOANS DEJECTEDLY)

134
00:16:28.988 --> 00:16:31.366
(BB-8 CHIRPING MERRILY)

135
00:16:33.576 --> 00:16:35.203
In the morning. you go.

136
00:16:36.954 --> 00:16:38.672
(BB-8 CHIRPS HAPPILY)

137
00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:42.126
You're welcome.

138
00:16:53.846 --> 00:16:55.098
<i>KYLO REN: I had no idea we had...</i>

139
00:16:55.181 --> 00:16:57.934
<i>the best pilot in
the Resistance on board.</i>

140
00:17:00.353 --> 00:17:01.354
<i>Comfortable?</i>

141
00:17:01.938 --> 00:17:02.939
Not really.

142
00:17:04.398 --> 00:17:05.695
<i>I'm impressed.</i>

143
00:17:08.194 --> 00:17:09.912
<i>No one has been able to
get out of you...</i>

144
00:17:10.613 --> 00:17:13.492
<i>what you did with the map.</i>

145
00:17:13.991 --> 00:17:16.335
You might want to rethink
your technique.

146
00:17:18.412 --> 00:17:20.210
(DULL HUMMING)

147
00:17:21.832 --> 00:17:23.049
(POE GRUNTS SOFTLY)

148
00:17:24.669 --> 00:17:26.387
(POE GROANING)

149
00:17:31.801 --> 00:17:34.145
<i>POE GRUNTS)
- Where is it?</i>

150
00:17:36.097 --> 00:17:37.724
(STRAINING) The Resistance...

151
00:17:37.807 --> 00:17:39.809
will not be intimidated by you.

152
00:17:43.980 --> 00:17:46.779
<i>Where... is it?</i>

153
00:17:47.400 --> 00:17:48.401
(GRUNTS)

154
00:17:52.321 --> 00:17:54.039
(YELLING)

155
00:17:56.742 --> 00:17:59.495
<i>It's in a droid. A BB unit.</i>

156
00:17:59.579 --> 00:18:02.048
Well. then. if it's on Jakku.
we'll soon have it.

157
00:18:02.123 --> 00:18:03.796
<i>I leave that to you.</i>

158
00:18:05.751 --> 00:18:08.630
REY: Don't give up hope.
He still might show up.

159
00:18:08.713 --> 00:18:10.841
Whoever it is you're waiting for.

160
00:18:10.923 --> 00:18:12.391
Classified.

161
00:18:13.092 --> 00:18:15.140
I know all about waiting.

162
00:18:15.344 --> 00:18:16.516
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

163
00:18:16.762 --> 00:18:18.184
For my family.

164
00:18:18.848 --> 00:18:21.601
They'll be back. One day.

165
00:18:22.393 --> 00:18:23.394
Come on.

166
00:18:26.397 --> 00:18:29.571
<i>UNKAR: These five pieces are worth...</i>

167
00:18:30.401 --> 00:18:32.529
Let me see here... hmm...

168
00:18:32.903 --> 00:18:35.622
one half portion.

169
00:18:35.698 --> 00:18:37.416
Last week they were a half portion each.

170
00:18:37.533 --> 00:18:39.206
What about the droid?

171
00:18:42.038 --> 00:18:43.085
What about him?

172
00:18:43.205 --> 00:18:45.378
I'll pay for him.

173
00:18:47.710 --> 00:18:50.054
-(METAL CLANKS)
-(NllMA TRADERS MURMURING)

174
00:18:51.255 --> 00:18:53.553
Sixty portions.

175
00:18:53.716 --> 00:18:55.559
(TRADERS EXCLAIMING)

176
00:19:05.561 --> 00:19:06.562
Actually...

177
00:19:08.564 --> 00:19:10.487
The droid's not for sale.

178
00:19:12.818 --> 00:19:13.819
Come on.

179
00:19:16.322 --> 00:19:18.040
-(METAL CLATTERS)
-(U N KAR GRU NTS)

180
00:19:18.115 --> 00:19:20.493
Follow the girl and get that droid.

181
00:19:24.330 --> 00:19:25.798
<i>FN-2187: Ren wants the prisoner.</i>

182
00:19:35.174 --> 00:19:36.300
<i>FN-2187". Turn here.</i>

183
00:19:38.260 --> 00:19:39.261
<i>Listen carefully.</i>

184
00:19:39.345 --> 00:19:41.598
<i>If you do exactly as I say.
I can get you out of here.</i>

185
00:19:41.681 --> 00:19:42.682
What?

186
00:19:43.933 --> 00:19:46.027
This is a rescue. I'm helping you escape.

187
00:19:46.102 --> 00:19:47.854
Can you fly a TIE fighter?

188
00:19:47.937 --> 00:19:48.984
You're with the Resistance?

189
00:19:49.105 --> 00:19:51.028
What? No. no. no. I'm breaking you out.

190
00:19:51.107 --> 00:19:53.109
- Can you fly a TIE fighter?
- I can fly anything.

191
00:19:53.859 --> 00:19:56.453
Why? Why are you helping me?

192
00:19:57.822 --> 00:19:59.540
Because it's the right thing to do.

193
00:20:00.449 --> 00:20:01.496
You need a pilot.

194
00:20:01.617 --> 00:20:02.960
I need a pilot.

195
00:20:04.453 --> 00:20:05.545
We're gonna do this.

196
00:20:05.871 --> 00:20:06.872
Yeah?

197
00:20:07.707 --> 00:20:09.004
(INDISTINCT PA CHATTER)

198
00:20:11.168 --> 00:20:13.387
<i>FN-2187: Okay. Stay calm. Stay calm.</i>

199
00:20:13.462 --> 00:20:15.965
- I <i>am calm.
- I'm talking to myself.</i>

200
00:20:18.467 --> 00:20:19.468
<i>FN-2187: Not yet.</i>

201
00:20:21.345 --> 00:20:23.063
<i>Okay. go. This way.</i>

202
00:20:29.311 --> 00:20:31.405
I've always wanted to fly
one of these things.

203
00:20:31.480 --> 00:20:33.574
- Can you shoot?
- Blasters. I can.

204
00:20:33.649 --> 00:20:34.992
Okay. same principle.

205
00:20:35.067 --> 00:20:36.068
Use the toggle on the left...

206
00:20:36.152 --> 00:20:37.825
to switch between missiles.
cannons and mag pulse.

207
00:20:37.945 --> 00:20:39.367
Use the sight on the right to aim.

208
00:20:39.780 --> 00:20:41.578
- Triggers to fire.
- This is very complicated.

209
00:20:42.992 --> 00:20:44.665
(ION ENGINES FIRING)

210
00:20:46.537 --> 00:20:48.005
(CABLE CLAN KS)

211
00:20:48.164 --> 00:20:49.256
POE: I can fix this.

212
00:20:52.585 --> 00:20:55.088
We have an unsanctioned
departure from bay two.

213
00:20:55.171 --> 00:20:57.924
Alert General Hux. And stop that fighter.

214
00:21:18.611 --> 00:21:19.703
OFFICER: Fourteen failed. Eighteen...

215
00:21:21.781 --> 00:21:22.873
POE: <i>I</i> got it.

216
00:21:24.575 --> 00:21:26.202
(ENGINES ROARING)

217
00:21:26.786 --> 00:21:28.333
(EXCLAIMS) This thing really moves.

218
00:21:32.917 --> 00:21:35.090
We gotta take out as many of
these cannons as we can...

219
00:21:35.252 --> 00:21:36.299
or we're not gonna get very far.

220
00:21:36.378 --> 00:21:37.800
- All right.
- I'm gonna get us in position.

221
00:21:37.880 --> 00:21:38.881
Just stay sharp.

222
00:21:42.092 --> 00:21:43.685
Up ahead! Up ahead! You see it?

223
00:21:43.761 --> 00:21:44.808
I got us dead center.

224
00:21:44.887 --> 00:21:46.013
-It's a clean shot.
- Okay. got it.

225
00:21:54.772 --> 00:21:56.194
- Yeah!
- Yes!

226
00:21:56.273 --> 00:21:57.365
(YELLING) Did you see that?

227
00:21:57.441 --> 00:21:59.068
- Did you see that?
- I saw it!

228
00:22:04.740 --> 00:22:05.866
Hey. what's your name?

229
00:22:05.950 --> 00:22:07.202
FN-2187.

230
00:22:07.284 --> 00:22:08.501
POE: F... What?

231
00:22:08.577 --> 00:22:10.420
That's the only name they ever gave me.

232
00:22:10.538 --> 00:22:13.007
Well. I ain't using it. F-N. huh?

233
00:22:13.082 --> 00:22:14.584
Finn. I'm gonna call you Finn.

234
00:22:14.667 --> 00:22:16.294
- Is that all right?
- Finn.

235
00:22:16.377 --> 00:22:18.050
Yeah. Finn. I like that.

236
00:22:18.128 --> 00:22:20.301
- I like that.
- I'm Poe. Poe Dameron.

237
00:22:20.381 --> 00:22:22.304
- Good to meet you. Poe.
- Good to meet you too. Finn.

238
00:22:24.426 --> 00:22:25.803
(ALARM BEEPING)

239
00:22:25.886 --> 00:22:28.309
OFFICER: Sir. they've
taken out our turbolasers.

240
00:22:29.098 --> 00:22:30.475
Use the ventral cannons.

241
00:22:30.808 --> 00:22:32.731
Yes. sir. Bringing them online.

242
00:22:32.810 --> 00:22:35.529
<i>KYLO REN". General Hux.
is it the Resistance pilot?</i>

243
00:22:35.604 --> 00:22:38.027
Yes. and he had help...

244
00:22:38.107 --> 00:22:39.484
from one of our own.

245
00:22:40.276 --> 00:22:41.493
We're checking the registers now...

246
00:22:41.610 --> 00:22:43.487
to identify which stormtrooper it was.

247
00:22:43.612 --> 00:22:46.991
<i>The one from the village. FN-2187.</i>

248
00:22:47.616 --> 00:22:49.414
Sir. ventral cannons hot.

249
00:22:49.952 --> 00:22:50.953
Fire.

250
00:23:00.337 --> 00:23:02.010
One's coming toward you!
My right. Your left.

251
00:23:02.089 --> 00:23:03.841
- Do you see it?
- Hold on.

252
00:23:03.966 --> 00:23:04.967
- I see him!
-(FIRING LASERS)

253
00:23:08.345 --> 00:23:09.847
Nice shot!

254
00:23:16.186 --> 00:23:17.278
Where are we going?

255
00:23:17.396 --> 00:23:18.522
We're going back to Jakku.
That's where.

256
00:23:18.647 --> 00:23:20.194
No. We can't go back to Jakku.

257
00:23:20.274 --> 00:23:21.742
We need to get out of this system.

258
00:23:21.817 --> 00:23:23.694
I gotta get my droid
before the First Order does.

259
00:23:23.819 --> 00:23:25.071
- What. a droid?
- That's right.

260
00:23:25.154 --> 00:23:27.373
He's a BB unit. orange and
white. One of a kind.

261
00:23:27.489 --> 00:23:28.490
I don't care what color he is!

262
00:23:28.574 --> 00:23:29.826
No droid can be that important.

263
00:23:29.909 --> 00:23:30.910
This one is. pal!

264
00:23:30.993 --> 00:23:32.666
We gotta get as far away from
the First Order as we can.

265
00:23:32.786 --> 00:23:34.083
We go back to Jakku. we die.

266
00:23:34.163 --> 00:23:36.882
That droid has a map
that leads straight to Luke Skywalker.

267
00:23:36.957 --> 00:23:38.880
Oh. you gotta be kidding me! (GRUNTS)

268
00:23:41.962 --> 00:23:45.057
<i>PHASMA: FN-2187 reported
to my division...</i>

269
00:23:45.174 --> 00:23:47.472
<i>was evaluated.
and sent to reconditioning.</i>

270
00:23:47.551 --> 00:23:49.804
No prior signs of nonconformity?

271
00:23:49.887 --> 00:23:51.810
<i>This was his first offense.</i>

272
00:23:51.889 --> 00:23:53.015
OFFICER: General!

273
00:23:53.098 --> 00:23:54.475
- They've been hit.
- Destroyed?

274
00:23:54.558 --> 00:23:55.810
Disabled.

275
00:23:55.893 --> 00:23:57.315
They were headed back to Jakku.

276
00:23:57.394 --> 00:23:59.613
The fighter is projected to
crash in the Goazon badlands.

277
00:23:59.688 --> 00:24:01.361
They were going back for the droid.

278
00:24:01.482 --> 00:24:03.405
Send a squad to the wreckage.

279
00:24:03.817 --> 00:24:05.194
(GASPS)

280
00:24:08.697 --> 00:24:09.698
(GROANS)

281
00:24:25.756 --> 00:24:26.928
FINN: (FAINTLY) Poe!

282
00:24:28.258 --> 00:24:29.555
POeI

283
00:24:30.386 --> 00:24:31.433
POeI

284
00:24:34.890 --> 00:24:36.392
Poe! I got you.

285
00:24:38.560 --> 00:24:39.561
POeI

286
00:24:41.105 --> 00:24:42.698
(SHIP CREAKING)

287
00:24:46.402 --> 00:24:47.449
POeI

288
00:25:55.512 --> 00:25:56.809
(PANTING)

289
00:26:11.653 --> 00:26:13.872
HUX: <i>Supreme Leader Snoke
was explicit.</i>

290
00:26:14.031 --> 00:26:16.454
Capture the droid if we can.
but destroy it if we must.

291
00:26:16.533 --> 00:26:18.331
<i>KYLO REN". How capable
are your soldiers. General?</i>

292
00:26:18.452 --> 00:26:19.920
I won't have you question my methods.

293
00:26:19.995 --> 00:26:22.043
<i>They're obviously skilled
at committing high treason.</i>

294
00:26:22.164 --> 00:26:24.963
<i>Perhaps Leader Snoke should
consider using a clone army.</i>

295
00:26:25.084 --> 00:26:26.131
My men are exceptionally trained.

296
00:26:26.210 --> 00:26:27.427
Programmed from birth.

297
00:26:27.503 --> 00:26:29.801
<i>Then they should have
no problem retrieving the droid.</i>

298
00:26:29.880 --> 00:26:30.881
<i>Unharmed.</i>

299
00:26:31.965 --> 00:26:34.138
Careful. Ren. that your
personal interests...

300
00:26:34.218 --> 00:26:36.687
not interfere with orders
from Leader Snoke.

301
00:26:36.845 --> 00:26:39.268
<i>I want that map.</i>

302
00:26:39.348 --> 00:26:40.725
<i>For your sake...</i>

303
00:26:40.849 --> 00:26:42.066
<i>I suggest you get it.</i>

304
00:26:48.649 --> 00:26:49.821
(PANTING) Water. Water.

305
00:26:49.900 --> 00:26:50.947
MERCHANT: (IN THICK ACCENT)
No water.

306
00:26:51.026 --> 00:26:52.528
- FINN: Water.
-(TRADER GRUNTS LOUDLY)

307
00:26:54.404 --> 00:26:55.496
(PANTS) ls there water?

308
00:26:55.572 --> 00:26:57.199
(MERCHANT EXCLAIMING
IN ALIEN DIALECT)

309
00:27:02.329 --> 00:27:03.876
(WATER SPLASHING)

310
00:27:15.050 --> 00:27:16.051
(SPUTTERING)

311
00:27:21.390 --> 00:27:23.768
(THUG SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

312
00:27:23.934 --> 00:27:26.278
- What? Oi. get off him!
-(BB-8 CHIRPS)

313
00:27:26.353 --> 00:27:27.730
-(REY YELPS)
-(THUG GROANS)

314
00:27:31.275 --> 00:27:32.492
-(BB-8 EXCLAIMS)
-(REY GRUNTS)

315
00:27:35.737 --> 00:27:36.738
Hey!

316
00:27:40.742 --> 00:27:41.743
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

317
00:27:45.414 --> 00:27:46.757
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

318
00:27:51.753 --> 00:27:53.005
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

319
00:27:53.130 --> 00:27:55.178
REY: They work for Unkar.

320
00:27:55.299 --> 00:27:57.051
That guy that wanted you.

321
00:27:57.134 --> 00:27:58.761
He must have really wanted you.

322
00:27:59.636 --> 00:28:00.933
(BB-8 EXCLAIMS LOUDLY)

323
00:28:01.138 --> 00:28:03.015
-(BB-8 CHIRPING)
- REYI Who?

324
00:28:03.932 --> 00:28:06.105
-(BB-8 CHIRPS EXCITEDLY)
- Him?

325
00:28:21.533 --> 00:28:22.659
(GRUNTS)

326
00:28:22.868 --> 00:28:24.040
(GROANS)

327
00:28:24.912 --> 00:28:28.086
- What's your hurry. thief?
- What? Thief?

328
00:28:28.248 --> 00:28:29.716
- Ow!

329
00:28:29.791 --> 00:28:31.088
- Hey. what?
- The jacket.

330
00:28:31.168 --> 00:28:32.670
This droid says you stole it.

331
00:28:33.629 --> 00:28:35.302
I've had a pretty messed up
day. all right?

332
00:28:35.422 --> 00:28:36.514
So I'd appreciate it...

333
00:28:36.632 --> 00:28:37.849
-if you stop accusing me of...
-(ZAPPING)

334
00:28:37.966 --> 00:28:40.389
- Ow! Stop it!
- Where'd you get it?

335
00:28:40.469 --> 00:28:41.812
It belongs to his master.

336
00:28:45.098 --> 00:28:48.193
It belonged to Poe Dameron.
That was his name. right?

337
00:28:50.229 --> 00:28:52.857
He was captured by the First Order.

338
00:28:52.981 --> 00:28:55.575
I helped him escape.
but our ship crashed.

339
00:28:58.695 --> 00:28:59.821
Poe didn't make it.

340
00:29:00.989 --> 00:29:02.366
(BB-8 MOANS DEJECTEDLY)

341
00:29:04.660 --> 00:29:06.833
I tried to help him. I'm sorry.

342
00:29:15.003 --> 00:29:16.721
So you're with the Resistance?

343
00:29:21.343 --> 00:29:22.686
Obviously.

344
00:29:22.844 --> 00:29:24.141
Yes. I am.

345
00:29:24.221 --> 00:29:25.518
I'm with the Resistance. yeah.

346
00:29:25.639 --> 00:29:27.687
(WHISPERS) I am with the Resistance.

347
00:29:28.892 --> 00:29:31.315
I've never met
a Resistance fighter before.

348
00:29:32.854 --> 00:29:34.322
Well. this is what we look like.

349
00:29:34.398 --> 00:29:36.947
Some of us. Others look different.

350
00:29:37.025 --> 00:29:38.493
BB-8 says he's on a secret mission.

351
00:29:38.568 --> 00:29:40.070
He has to get back to your base.

352
00:29:40.195 --> 00:29:42.448
Apparently. he has a map that
leads to Luke Skywalker...

353
00:29:42.531 --> 00:29:44.204
and everyone's after it.

354
00:29:44.825 --> 00:29:46.543
(WHISPERS) Luke Skywalker?

355
00:29:47.077 --> 00:29:48.579
I thought he was a myth.

356
00:29:48.787 --> 00:29:50.881
-(BB-8 CHIRPING RAPIDLY)
- What?

357
00:29:54.835 --> 00:29:56.803
(THUG SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

358
00:29:58.880 --> 00:30:00.427
- What are you doing?
- Come on.

359
00:30:01.717 --> 00:30:02.889
FINN: Come on. BB-8!

360
00:30:06.221 --> 00:30:07.723
- REY: Let go of me!
- Come on. we gotta move!

361
00:30:07.848 --> 00:30:09.942
I know how to run
without you holding my hand!

362
00:30:12.519 --> 00:30:14.317
REY: BB-8. stay close!

363
00:30:14.396 --> 00:30:15.397
This way.

364
00:30:17.232 --> 00:30:18.984
(TRADERS SHOUTING
IN ALIEN DIALECT)

365
00:30:21.194 --> 00:30:22.411
<i>ST ORMTROOPER:
Call in the air strike.</i>

366
00:30:23.238 --> 00:30:24.785
FINN: Come on!

367
00:30:26.241 --> 00:30:27.458
REY: They're shooting at both of us.

368
00:30:27.576 --> 00:30:29.453
Yeah. They saw you with me.
You're marked.

369
00:30:29.578 --> 00:30:31.000
- Well. thanks for that.
- Hey!

370
00:30:31.079 --> 00:30:32.922
I'm not the one who chased
you down with a stick.

371
00:30:33.040 --> 00:30:34.087
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

372
00:30:34.207 --> 00:30:35.709
(SHOUTING) Does anyone have
blasters around here?

373
00:30:35.792 --> 00:30:37.339
- Are you okay?
-(BB-8 CHIRPING)

374
00:30:37.419 --> 00:30:38.716
(FINN SHUSHING)

375
00:30:38.795 --> 00:30:41.048
(DISTANT ION ENGINES ROARING)

376
00:30:42.883 --> 00:30:44.305
Stop taking my hand!

377
00:30:47.763 --> 00:30:48.889
(BOTH GRUNTING)

378
00:30:51.850 --> 00:30:53.397
(ALL CLAMORING)

379
00:30:53.477 --> 00:30:55.104
(ENGINES ROARING)

380
00:31:00.609 --> 00:31:01.610
Hey-

381
00:31:03.070 --> 00:31:04.071
(GRUNTS)

382
00:31:04.905 --> 00:31:05.952
Are you okay?

383
00:31:07.949 --> 00:31:08.950
Yeah.

384
00:31:09.618 --> 00:31:10.744
Follow me.

385
00:31:22.297 --> 00:31:23.549
- FINN: We can't outrun them!
- We might...

386
00:31:23.632 --> 00:31:24.929
in that quadjumper!

387
00:31:25.008 --> 00:31:26.351
Hey. we need a pilot!

388
00:31:26.468 --> 00:31:28.015
We've got one.

389
00:31:28.136 --> 00:31:29.137
You?

390
00:31:29.805 --> 00:31:31.773
Uh. what about that ship?

391
00:31:31.848 --> 00:31:33.316
That one's garbage!

392
00:31:38.814 --> 00:31:40.282
The garbage will do.

393
00:31:50.158 --> 00:31:51.455
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

394
00:31:56.164 --> 00:31:57.882
Gunner position is down there!

395
00:32:01.128 --> 00:32:02.755
You ever fly this thing?

396
00:32:02.879 --> 00:32:06.008
No! This ship hasn't flown in years.

397
00:32:06.174 --> 00:32:07.175
Great.

398
00:32:11.388 --> 00:32:12.605
Whoa.

399
00:32:13.223 --> 00:32:14.816
I can do this. I can do this.

400
00:32:15.225 --> 00:32:16.852
I can do this. I can do this.

401
00:32:18.728 --> 00:32:20.025
(THRUSTERS FIRING)

402
00:32:29.990 --> 00:32:31.458
-(REY YELPS)
-(FINN GRUNTS)

403
00:32:38.039 --> 00:32:39.040
UNKAR: Hey!

404
00:32:43.378 --> 00:32:44.925
That's mine!

405
00:32:48.508 --> 00:32:50.101
Wait. stay low! Hey. stay low!

406
00:32:50.218 --> 00:32:51.310
- What?
- FINN: (on RADIO) Stay <i>low!</i>

407
00:32:51.386 --> 00:32:52.603
It confuses their tracking.

408
00:32:52.971 --> 00:32:54.894
- BB-8. hold on!
-(BB-8 CHIRPS)

409
00:32:55.056 --> 00:32:56.433
I'm going low!

410
00:33:04.608 --> 00:33:06.576
-(REY GASPS)
-(BB-8 EXCLAIMS)

411
00:33:13.867 --> 00:33:14.914
(GRUNTS)

412
00:33:15.076 --> 00:33:16.293
What are you doing back there?

413
00:33:16.411 --> 00:33:17.583
Are you ever gonna fire back?

414
00:33:17.746 --> 00:33:19.794
I'm working on it! Are the shields up?

415
00:33:19.915 --> 00:33:21.588
Not so easy without a co-pilot!

416
00:33:21.750 --> 00:33:23.627
Try sitting in this thing.

417
00:33:26.379 --> 00:33:27.505
(REY GRUNTS)

418
00:33:31.468 --> 00:33:32.720
(LASERS FIRING)

419
00:33:37.933 --> 00:33:39.276
We need cover. quick!

420
00:33:39.434 --> 00:33:40.731
We're about to get some!

421
00:33:40.810 --> 00:33:42.027
(SOFTLY) <i>I</i> hope.

422
00:33:42.187 --> 00:33:43.404
(HULL CREAKING)

423
00:34:07.712 --> 00:34:09.214
Damn it!

424
00:34:13.260 --> 00:34:14.762
(ENGINE REVVING)

425
00:34:20.183 --> 00:34:21.981
Come on. come on!

426
00:34:24.813 --> 00:34:27.066
- Nice shot!
- I'm getting pretty good at this.

427
00:34:29.776 --> 00:34:31.403
(SCAVENGER EXCLAIMING
IN ALIEN DIALECT)

428
00:34:39.286 --> 00:34:41.004
(CONTROLS CLICKING)

429
00:34:41.079 --> 00:34:42.706
Uh. the cannon's stuck
in forward position.

430
00:34:42.789 --> 00:34:44.462
I can't move it. You gotta lose him!

431
00:34:44.624 --> 00:34:45.796
(REY PANTING)

432
00:34:48.336 --> 00:34:50.839
- Get ready!
- Okay. For what?

433
00:35:04.644 --> 00:35:05.770
Are we really doing this?

434
00:35:12.277 --> 00:35:13.369
(REY GRUNTS)

435
00:35:15.196 --> 00:35:16.539
Oh. no.

436
00:35:37.969 --> 00:35:38.970
Whoo!

437
00:35:53.360 --> 00:35:54.862
- REY: Nice shooting.
- Now that was some flying.

438
00:35:54.944 --> 00:35:55.945
- Thanks.
- How did you do that?

439
00:35:56.029 --> 00:35:57.326
- I don't know.
- No one trained you?

440
00:35:57.405 --> 00:35:59.157
I've flown some ships. but
I've never left the planet.

441
00:35:59.240 --> 00:36:00.412
- Your last shot was dead-on.
- That was amazing.

442
00:36:00.492 --> 00:36:01.835
- You got him with one blast!
- You set me up for it.

443
00:36:01.910 --> 00:36:03.287
- It was perfect.
- That was pretty good.

444
00:36:03.370 --> 00:36:04.371
(CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

445
00:36:04.996 --> 00:36:06.794
(CHIRPS NERVOUSLY)

446
00:36:06.915 --> 00:36:08.917
You're okay. He's with the Resistance.

447
00:36:10.293 --> 00:36:11.920
He's gonna get you home.

448
00:36:13.046 --> 00:36:14.047
We both will.

449
00:36:19.886 --> 00:36:21.012
I don't know your name.

450
00:36:22.972 --> 00:36:24.519
Finn. What's yours?

451
00:36:25.809 --> 00:36:27.106
I'm Rey.

452
00:36:31.648 --> 00:36:32.991
- Rey...
-(PIPE BURSTING)

453
00:36:33.608 --> 00:36:35.906
REY: Help me with this. Quick!

454
00:36:35.985 --> 00:36:37.362
FINN: Whoa. what's going on?

455
00:36:37.487 --> 00:36:38.909
(REY GRUNTS)

456
00:36:48.623 --> 00:36:49.795
Sir...

457
00:36:49.874 --> 00:36:52.502
we were unable to acquire
the droid on Jakku.

458
00:36:54.963 --> 00:36:56.135
It escaped capture...

459
00:36:56.214 --> 00:36:58.808
aboard a stolen
Corellian YT model freighter.

460
00:37:00.343 --> 00:37:02.437
<i>The droid...</i>

461
00:37:02.512 --> 00:37:04.139
<i>stole a freighter?</i>

462
00:37:04.264 --> 00:37:05.641
Not exactly. sir.

463
00:37:06.307 --> 00:37:07.308
It had help.

464
00:37:10.937 --> 00:37:12.029
We have no confirmation...

465
00:37:12.147 --> 00:37:14.525
but we believe FN-2187 may
have helped in the escape.

466
00:37:14.983 --> 00:37:16.200
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

467
00:37:16.317 --> 00:37:17.864
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

468
00:37:21.906 --> 00:37:23.749
(INSTRUMENTS SMASHING)

469
00:37:30.123 --> 00:37:31.500
(LIGHTSABER DEACTIVATING)

470
00:37:32.876 --> 00:37:33.877
<i>Anything else?</i>

471
00:37:36.755 --> 00:37:38.177
The two were accompanied by a girl.

472
00:37:40.425 --> 00:37:41.847
(CHOKING)

473
00:37:43.595 --> 00:37:45.347
<i>What girl?</i>

474
00:37:45.680 --> 00:37:47.307
(INSTRUMENTS BEEPING RAPIDLY)

475
00:37:48.057 --> 00:37:49.149
It's the motivator.

476
00:37:49.225 --> 00:37:50.727
Grab me a Harris wrench.
check in there.

477
00:37:50.810 --> 00:37:51.811
How bad is it?

478
00:37:51.895 --> 00:37:53.568
If we wanna live. not good.

479
00:37:53.688 --> 00:37:54.655
They're hunting for us now.

480
00:37:54.731 --> 00:37:55.903
We've gotta get out of this system!

481
00:37:56.024 --> 00:37:57.526
BB-8 said the location
of the Resistance base...

482
00:37:57.692 --> 00:37:58.739
is "need to know".

483
00:37:58.860 --> 00:38:00.487
If I'm taking you there. I need to know!

484
00:38:00.570 --> 00:38:01.571
This?

485
00:38:02.822 --> 00:38:04.449
(QUIETLY) You gotta tell us
where your base is.

486
00:38:04.574 --> 00:38:07.168
-(BB-8 CHIRPS)
- I don't speak that.

487
00:38:07.243 --> 00:38:08.995
(WHISPERS) All right. between us...

488
00:38:09.078 --> 00:38:10.546
I'm not with the Resistance. okay?

489
00:38:11.539 --> 00:38:13.132
I'm just trying to get away
from the First Order.

490
00:38:13.208 --> 00:38:14.960
But you tell us where the base is...

491
00:38:15.043 --> 00:38:16.465
I'll get you there first. Deal?

492
00:38:17.545 --> 00:38:20.048
- Droid. please!
- Pilex driver. hurry.

493
00:38:20.173 --> 00:38:22.801
- So. where's your base?
- Go on. BB-8. tell her.

494
00:38:26.012 --> 00:38:27.013
(WHISPERS) Please.

495
00:38:27.555 --> 00:38:28.932
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

496
00:38:29.057 --> 00:38:30.934
- The lleenium system?
- Yeah. the lleenium system.

497
00:38:31.059 --> 00:38:32.686
That's the one. Get us there
as fast as you can.

498
00:38:33.061 --> 00:38:34.404
I'll drop you two at Ponemah Terminal.

499
00:38:34.562 --> 00:38:35.654
I need the bonding tape. hurry!

500
00:38:35.730 --> 00:38:36.822
What about you?

501
00:38:36.898 --> 00:38:38.115
I gotta get back to Jakku.

502
00:38:38.233 --> 00:38:39.200
Back to Jak...

503
00:38:39.275 --> 00:38:40.743
Why does everyone
wanna go back to Jakku?

504
00:38:40.819 --> 00:38:43.413
-It's not that one. No. No.
- That place is...

505
00:38:43.530 --> 00:38:45.407
The one I'm pointing to. No.

506
00:38:45.490 --> 00:38:46.787
(LOUDLY) No. No!

507
00:38:46.908 --> 00:38:48.251
If we don't patch it up...

508
00:38:48.409 --> 00:38:49.456
the propulsion tank will overflow...

509
00:38:49.536 --> 00:38:51.209
and flood the ship with poisonous gas!

510
00:38:51.287 --> 00:38:52.288
- This?
- Yes.

511
00:38:53.665 --> 00:38:56.509
Hey. Rey. you're a pilot.

512
00:38:56.584 --> 00:38:58.507
You can fly anywhere. Why go back?

513
00:38:58.586 --> 00:38:59.883
You got a family?

514
00:38:59.963 --> 00:39:01.089
You got a boyfriend? A cute boyfriend?

515
00:39:01.214 --> 00:39:02.682
None of your business. that's why.

516
00:39:02.757 --> 00:39:04.225
(POWER DRAINING)

517
00:39:05.093 --> 00:39:06.470
- That can't be good.
- No. it can't be.

518
00:39:10.348 --> 00:39:11.395
(FLICKING SWITCHES)

519
00:39:12.433 --> 00:39:13.434
Someone's locked on to us.

520
00:39:13.560 --> 00:39:15.107
All controls are overridden.

521
00:39:15.395 --> 00:39:16.487
(DULL CLANGING)

522
00:39:21.901 --> 00:39:23.619
Get off! Get off!

523
00:39:25.363 --> 00:39:26.364
See anything?

524
00:39:27.824 --> 00:39:28.825
FINN: Oh. no.

525
00:39:37.083 --> 00:39:38.084
It's the First Order.

526
00:39:38.167 --> 00:39:39.965
What do we do?
There must be something.

527
00:39:40.753 --> 00:39:42.426
- You said poisonous gas.
- I fixed that.

528
00:39:42.505 --> 00:39:43.506
Can you unfix it?

529
00:39:49.304 --> 00:39:50.305
REY: Come on. BB-8.

530
00:39:51.055 --> 00:39:52.932
FINN: I got him. (YELPS)

531
00:39:54.267 --> 00:39:56.019
-(POWER RETURNING)
- FINN: I'm okay.

532
00:39:56.853 --> 00:39:58.400
-(REY STRAINING)
- FINN: BB-8. get off me!

533
00:39:58.521 --> 00:40:00.489
-(BB-8 CHIRPING)
-(DULL THUDDING)

534
00:40:01.274 --> 00:40:02.947
Do you think this will work
on the stormtroopers?

535
00:40:03.026 --> 00:40:05.575
Yeah. Their masks filter out
smoke. not toxins.

536
00:40:09.198 --> 00:40:11.246
-(METAL CLANGING)
-(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

537
00:40:12.952 --> 00:40:14.124
- FINN: Hurry.
- I'm hurrying.

538
00:40:16.539 --> 00:40:17.711
(METAL WHIRRING)

539
00:40:26.215 --> 00:40:28.638
Chewie...

540
00:40:28.718 --> 00:40:29.970
we're home.

541
00:40:30.553 --> 00:40:32.100
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

542
00:40:35.642 --> 00:40:37.269
(CH EWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

543
00:40:37.769 --> 00:40:38.861
-(FLICKS SWITCH)
-(CONTROLS BEEP)

544
00:40:39.020 --> 00:40:40.192
(OBJECT CLATTERS)

545
00:40:45.985 --> 00:40:47.157
Where are the others?

546
00:40:47.236 --> 00:40:48.829
- Where's the pilot?
- REY: I'm the <i>pilot.</i>

547
00:40:48.905 --> 00:40:50.373
- You?
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)

548
00:40:50.448 --> 00:40:52.416
<i>No. it's true.
We're the only ones on board.</i>

549
00:40:52.492 --> 00:40:53.914
<i>FINN: You can understand that thing?</i>

550
00:40:54.035 --> 00:40:55.161
And "that thing"
can understand you. too...

551
00:40:55.244 --> 00:40:56.291
so watch it.

552
00:40:56.371 --> 00:40:58.294
- Come on out of there.
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)

553
00:40:58.998 --> 00:41:00.875
- Where'd you get this ship?
- Niima Outpost.

554
00:41:01.000 --> 00:41:03.549
Jakku? Thatjunkyard?

555
00:41:03.628 --> 00:41:04.845
Thank you! Junkyard.

556
00:41:04.921 --> 00:41:07.015
Told you we should have
double-checked the Western Reaches.

557
00:41:07.090 --> 00:41:08.842
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)
- Who had it? Ducain?

558
00:41:08.925 --> 00:41:10.768
REY: I stole it. From Unkar Plutt.

559
00:41:10.843 --> 00:41:13.062
He stole it from the Irving Boys.
who stole it from Ducain.

560
00:41:13.179 --> 00:41:15.477
Who stole it from me!

561
00:41:15.556 --> 00:41:16.978
Well. you tell him that Han Solo...

562
00:41:17.058 --> 00:41:19.436
just stole back the
Millennium Falcon for good.

563
00:41:19.560 --> 00:41:22.439
<i>This</i> is <i>the Millennium Falcon?
You're Han Solo?</i>

564
00:41:24.065 --> 00:41:25.612
I used to be.

565
00:41:26.275 --> 00:41:27.743
Han Solo. the Rebellion general?

566
00:41:27.819 --> 00:41:29.196
No. the smuggler.

567
00:41:29.278 --> 00:41:31.121
- Wasn't he a war hero?
-(CHEWIE GRUNTS)

568
00:41:31.197 --> 00:41:34.542
This is the ship that made
the Kessel Run in 14 parsecs?

569
00:41:34.617 --> 00:41:35.869
Twelve!

570
00:41:36.953 --> 00:41:38.421
(SCOFFS) Fourteen.

571
00:41:53.761 --> 00:41:54.933
Hey!

572
00:41:55.430 --> 00:41:58.434
Some moof-milker
put a compressor on the ignition line.

573
00:41:58.516 --> 00:41:59.608
REY: Unkar Plutt did.

574
00:41:59.684 --> 00:42:01.061
I thought it was a mistake.
too. Puts too much...

575
00:42:01.144 --> 00:42:03.442
BOTH: ...stress on the hyperdrive.

576
00:42:04.480 --> 00:42:05.948
Chewie. throw them in a pod.

577
00:42:06.065 --> 00:42:07.942
We'll drop them at the
nearest inhabited planet.

578
00:42:08.026 --> 00:42:09.744
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)
- REY: Wait. no.

579
00:42:09.819 --> 00:42:12.242
- We need your help.
- My help?

580
00:42:12.321 --> 00:42:13.868
This droid has to get
to the Resistance base...

581
00:42:13.948 --> 00:42:15.245
as soon as possible.

582
00:42:15.950 --> 00:42:18.328
He's carrying a map to Luke Skywalker.

583
00:42:22.832 --> 00:42:25.756
You are the Han Solo that
fought with the Rebellion.

584
00:42:31.841 --> 00:42:32.842
You knew him.

585
00:42:36.179 --> 00:42:39.308
Yeah. I knew him.

586
00:42:39.390 --> 00:42:41.017
I knew Luke.

587
00:42:41.601 --> 00:42:42.602
(DULL THUDDING)

588
00:42:43.811 --> 00:42:46.109
Don't tell me a Rathtar's gotten loose.

589
00:42:46.773 --> 00:42:47.774
FINN: Wait. what?

590
00:42:48.691 --> 00:42:50.364
Did you just say Rathtars?

591
00:42:51.110 --> 00:42:52.111
Hey!

592
00:42:52.195 --> 00:42:54.744
You're not hauling Rathtars
on this freighter. are you?

593
00:42:55.281 --> 00:42:57.500
- I'm hauling Rathtars.
-(CHEWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

594
00:42:57.575 --> 00:43:00.795
Oh. great. It's the Guavian Death Gang.

595
00:43:00.870 --> 00:43:02.338
Must have tracked us from Nantoon.

596
00:43:02.455 --> 00:43:04.253
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)
- What's a Rathtar?

597
00:43:04.332 --> 00:43:05.834
They're big and they're dangerous.

598
00:43:05.917 --> 00:43:07.464
You ever heard of the Trillia Massacre?

599
00:43:07.543 --> 00:43:08.590
- No.
- FINN: Good.

600
00:43:08.669 --> 00:43:10.546
I got three of them going to King Prana.

601
00:43:10.630 --> 00:43:12.974
Three? How'd you get them on board?

602
00:43:13.049 --> 00:43:14.767
I used to have a bigger crew.

603
00:43:15.259 --> 00:43:16.306
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

604
00:43:16.427 --> 00:43:18.179
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

605
00:43:18.346 --> 00:43:20.269
HAN: Get below and stay there
until I say so...

606
00:43:20.348 --> 00:43:21.941
and don't even think about
taking the Falcon.

607
00:43:22.016 --> 00:43:23.017
What about BB-8?

608
00:43:23.101 --> 00:43:24.819
He stays with me
until I get rid of the gang...

609
00:43:24.894 --> 00:43:26.441
then you can have him back
and be on your way.

610
00:43:26.521 --> 00:43:28.489
What about the Rathtars?
Where are you keeping them?

611
00:43:28.564 --> 00:43:29.986
-(LOUD THUDDING)
-(BOTH YELP)

612
00:43:30.900 --> 00:43:32.948
- There's one.
- What are you gonna do?

613
00:43:33.027 --> 00:43:35.325
Same thing I always do.
Talk my way out of it.

614
00:43:35.404 --> 00:43:36.576
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

615
00:43:36.656 --> 00:43:38.909
Yes. I do. Every time.

616
00:43:56.175 --> 00:43:58.177
Han Solo.

617
00:43:58.261 --> 00:43:59.729
You're a dead man.

618
00:43:59.846 --> 00:44:02.565
Bala-Tik. What's the problem?

619
00:44:02.765 --> 00:44:05.439
The problem is we loaned you
50.000 for this job.

620
00:44:05.601 --> 00:44:08.070
-(WHISPERS) Can you see them?
- No.

621
00:44:08.229 --> 00:44:11.233
I heard you also borrowed
50.000 from Kanjiklub.

622
00:44:11.440 --> 00:44:13.568
You know you can't trust
those little freaks.

623
00:44:14.235 --> 00:44:16.658
How long we known each other?

624
00:44:16.737 --> 00:44:17.829
They have blasters.

625
00:44:17.905 --> 00:44:18.997
A lot of them.

626
00:44:19.073 --> 00:44:22.293
BALA-TIK: Not long.
We want our money back now.

627
00:44:22.368 --> 00:44:24.370
HAN: You think hunting
Rathtars is cheap?

628
00:44:24.453 --> 00:44:25.625
I spent that money.

629
00:44:25.705 --> 00:44:28.128
Kanjiklub wants
their investment back. too.

630
00:44:28.249 --> 00:44:30.547
I never made a deal with Kanjiklub!

631
00:44:30.626 --> 00:44:32.503
BALA-TIKZ Tell that t0 Kanjiklub.

632
00:44:32.587 --> 00:44:34.009
(AIRLOCK CLAN KING)

633
00:44:41.804 --> 00:44:44.023
Tasu Leech.

634
00:44:44.098 --> 00:44:45.099
Good to see you.

635
00:44:45.558 --> 00:44:47.356
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

636
00:44:49.353 --> 00:44:51.230
(CONTINUES SPEAKING
ALIEN DIALECT)

637
00:44:53.941 --> 00:44:56.945
Boys. you're both gonna
get what I promised.

638
00:44:57.028 --> 00:44:58.405
Have I ever not delivered...

639
00:44:58.487 --> 00:44:59.989
-for you before?
- Yeah.

640
00:45:04.285 --> 00:45:07.289
- What was the second time?
- BALA-TIK: Your game is old.

641
00:45:07.413 --> 00:45:09.916
There's no one in the galaxy
left for you to swindle.

642
00:45:12.585 --> 00:45:13.586
That BB unit.

643
00:45:13.669 --> 00:45:16.513
The First Order is looking
for one just like it.

644
00:45:20.009 --> 00:45:21.306
And two fugitives.

645
00:45:25.181 --> 00:45:26.307
First I've heard of it.

646
00:45:32.146 --> 00:45:33.318
REY: Wait. wait. wait.

647
00:45:36.484 --> 00:45:38.532
If we close the blast doors
in that corridor...

648
00:45:38.653 --> 00:45:39.779
we can trap both gangs!

649
00:45:39.862 --> 00:45:41.330
We'll close the blast doors from here?

650
00:45:41.405 --> 00:45:43.203
Resetting the fuses should do it.

651
00:45:46.369 --> 00:45:47.996
(RATHTARS GROWLING)

652
00:45:48.621 --> 00:45:50.089
(RATHTARS ROARING FAINTLY)

653
00:45:51.165 --> 00:45:52.963
I got a bad feeling about this.

654
00:45:53.042 --> 00:45:55.170
- Oh. no.
-"Oh. no." what?

655
00:45:56.128 --> 00:45:57.129
Wrong fuses.

656
00:45:57.213 --> 00:45:58.385
- Kill them!
-(BLASTERS COCKING)

657
00:45:58.506 --> 00:45:59.723
- Whoa...
- And take the droid!

658
00:46:00.341 --> 00:46:02.343
-(THUGS SCREAMING)
-(RATHTAR GROWLING)

659
00:46:05.179 --> 00:46:07.022
(THUGS CLAMORING)

660
00:46:09.892 --> 00:46:11.189
(CHEWIE YELPS)

661
00:46:13.062 --> 00:46:14.530
(RATHTAR SCREECHING)

662
00:46:17.566 --> 00:46:18.738
(THUG GROANS)

663
00:46:19.527 --> 00:46:20.949
(RATHTAR ROARS)

664
00:46:23.823 --> 00:46:24.824
<i>(RAT HT AR BELCHES)</i>

665
00:46:25.533 --> 00:46:27.376
- This was a mistake!
- Huge!

666
00:46:27.535 --> 00:46:29.037
(THUG YELLING)

667
00:46:35.084 --> 00:46:37.052
(RATHTAR ROARS FAINTLY)

668
00:46:40.589 --> 00:46:41.590
REY: What do they look like?

669
00:46:43.884 --> 00:46:45.636
-(RATHTAR GROWLING)
-(THUG SCREAMING)

670
00:46:47.555 --> 00:46:49.557
They look like that.

671
00:46:51.809 --> 00:46:53.652
- FINN: This way.
- Are you sure?

672
00:46:55.563 --> 00:46:56.735
No.no.no!

673
00:46:57.773 --> 00:46:59.150
- Finn!
-(YELPS)

674
00:47:00.151 --> 00:47:01.243
Finn!

675
00:47:02.403 --> 00:47:03.404
Rey!

676
00:47:05.281 --> 00:47:06.498
(REY YELPS)

677
00:47:06.574 --> 00:47:07.871
FINN: Get Off! Get Off!

678
00:47:10.953 --> 00:47:12.250
(RATHTAR HOWLS FAINTLY)

679
00:47:13.289 --> 00:47:15.633
-(FAINTLY) Rey!
- Finn!

680
00:47:16.834 --> 00:47:17.926
Finn!

681
00:47:18.586 --> 00:47:20.259
FINN: (FAINTLY ON MONITOR)
<i>Get</i> off me!

682
00:47:22.131 --> 00:47:23.474
(FINN GROANING FAINTLY)

683
00:47:27.094 --> 00:47:29.392
-(MONITOR BEEPING)
-(FINN SCREAMING FAINTLY)

684
00:47:31.932 --> 00:47:33.434
FIN NI (FAINTLY) <i>Rey!</i>

685
00:47:34.393 --> 00:47:35.770
(FINN YELLING)

686
00:47:36.479 --> 00:47:39.358
-(RATHTAR ROARS FAINTLY)
- Get off! Get off!

687
00:47:40.608 --> 00:47:41.655
(GRUNTING)

688
00:47:41.776 --> 00:47:43.278
- Finn!
-(SHRIEKS)

689
00:47:43.944 --> 00:47:46.288
- It had me! But the door...
- That was lucky.

690
00:47:50.326 --> 00:47:52.624
- I got the door. Cover us!
-(CHEWIE ROARS)

691
00:47:56.499 --> 00:47:57.625
(BB-8 YELPS)

692
00:47:59.460 --> 00:48:01.337
-(CHEWIE ROARS)
- Chewie!

693
00:48:04.215 --> 00:48:05.808
- You okay?
-(CHEWIE GRUNTS)

694
00:48:06.967 --> 00:48:07.968
Wow.

695
00:48:10.179 --> 00:48:12.398
- Come on! Come on!
-(CHEWIE EXCLAIMS)

696
00:48:16.143 --> 00:48:17.144
Han.

697
00:48:17.228 --> 00:48:19.481
You. close the door behind us.
You. take care of Chewie!

698
00:48:19.855 --> 00:48:20.902
(CHEWIE ROARS)

699
00:48:21.565 --> 00:48:23.988
-(FLICKING SWITCHES)
-(SHIP POWERING UP)

700
00:48:27.154 --> 00:48:28.406
Hey. where are you going?

701
00:48:28.489 --> 00:48:30.162
Unkar Plutt installed a fuel pump. too.

702
00:48:30.241 --> 00:48:32.039
If we don't prime that.
we're not going anywhere.

703
00:48:32.159 --> 00:48:33.331
I hate that guy.

704
00:48:33.452 --> 00:48:35.955
- And you could use a co-pilot.
- I got one. he's back there.

705
00:48:36.038 --> 00:48:37.039
(CHEWIE GROANS)

706
00:48:38.416 --> 00:48:40.384
Watch the thrust. We're going
out of here at lightspeed.

707
00:48:40.501 --> 00:48:42.299
From inside the hangar?
Is that even possible?

708
00:48:42.378 --> 00:48:44.631
I never ask that question
till after I've done it.

709
00:48:44.713 --> 00:48:46.511
<i>RAT HT AR GROW LS)
{REY YELP S';</i>

710
00:48:46.882 --> 00:48:49.010
This is not how I thought
this day was gonna go.

711
00:48:49.135 --> 00:48:51.103
Angle the shield. Hang on back there.

712
00:48:51.178 --> 00:48:52.350
No problem!

713
00:49:02.273 --> 00:49:03.525
Come on. baby. don't let me down.

714
00:49:06.068 --> 00:49:08.036
- What?
- Compressor.

715
00:49:09.155 --> 00:49:10.782
(THRUSTERS FIRING)

716
00:49:12.867 --> 00:49:14.414
(LOUD BOOMING)

717
00:49:16.537 --> 00:49:17.754
Inform the First Order...

718
00:49:17.830 --> 00:49:19.673
that Han Solo has the droid they want.

719
00:49:19.748 --> 00:49:21.750
<i>And it's</i> aboard <i>the Millennium Falcon.</i>

720
00:49:23.127 --> 00:49:24.925
(ION ENGINES ROARING)

721
00:49:30.676 --> 00:49:35.056
<i>SNOKE: The droid will soon be
delivered to the Resistance...</i>

722
00:49:36.265 --> 00:49:40.065
leading them to the last Jedi.

723
00:49:41.270 --> 00:49:45.025
If Skywalker returns...

724
00:49:45.566 --> 00:49:49.571
the new Jedi will rise.

725
00:49:50.738 --> 00:49:52.285
Supreme Leader.
I take full responsibility...

726
00:49:52.406 --> 00:49:54.079
General!

727
00:49:56.285 --> 00:49:59.084
Our strategy must now change.

728
00:49:59.205 --> 00:50:01.253
The weapon. It is ready.

729
00:50:01.373 --> 00:50:03.626
I believe the time has come to use it.

730
00:50:03.751 --> 00:50:05.048
We shall destroy the government...

731
00:50:05.127 --> 00:50:06.549
that supports the Resistance...

732
00:50:06.629 --> 00:50:08.347
the Republic.

733
00:50:08.422 --> 00:50:09.969
Without their friends to protect them...

734
00:50:10.049 --> 00:50:11.642
the Resistance will be vulnerable.

735
00:50:11.884 --> 00:50:14.808
And we will stop them
before they reach Skywalker.

736
00:50:14.887 --> 00:50:16.139
Go.

737
00:50:16.931 --> 00:50:18.353
Oversee preparations.

738
00:50:18.432 --> 00:50:20.105
Yes. Supreme Leader.

739
00:50:26.065 --> 00:50:27.442
SNOKE: There has been an awakening.

740
00:50:29.151 --> 00:50:30.903
Have you felt it?

741
00:50:32.446 --> 00:50:33.493
KYLO REN: Yes.

742
00:50:34.865 --> 00:50:36.492
There's something more.

743
00:50:38.035 --> 00:50:42.211
<i>The</i> droid <i>we</i> seek <i>is</i> aboard
<i>the Millennium Falcon.</i>

744
00:50:42.998 --> 00:50:45.877
In the hands of your father...

745
00:50:45.960 --> 00:50:49.806
Han Solo.

746
00:50:52.424 --> 00:50:54.802
<i>He means nothing to me.</i>

747
00:50:54.927 --> 00:50:59.728
Even you. master of the
Knights of Ren...

748
00:51:00.349 --> 00:51:03.819
have never faced such a test.

749
00:51:04.436 --> 00:51:07.656
<i>By the grace of your training.
I will not be seduced.</i>

750
00:51:08.774 --> 00:51:10.617
We shall see.

751
00:51:13.195 --> 00:51:15.038
We shall see.

752
00:51:21.870 --> 00:51:22.996
(FUSE BLOWING)

753
00:51:23.122 --> 00:51:25.341
- Electrical overload.
- I can fix that.

754
00:51:25.457 --> 00:51:26.709
Coolant's leaking.

755
00:51:26.834 --> 00:51:27.960
(ALARM BEEPING)

756
00:51:28.043 --> 00:51:29.295
Try transferring auxiliary power...

757
00:51:29.420 --> 00:51:30.797
BOTH:...to the secondary tank.

758
00:51:30.879 --> 00:51:32.426
- I got it.
-(CHEWIE GROWLING)

759
00:51:32.590 --> 00:51:34.217
FINN: Chewie. come on!

760
00:51:35.843 --> 00:51:37.436
I need help with this giant hairy thing!

761
00:51:37.511 --> 00:51:38.512
- Stop moving!
-(BB-8 CHIRPS)

762
00:51:38.637 --> 00:51:40.480
-(CHEWIE ROARS)
-(BB-8 YELPS)

763
00:51:40.556 --> 00:51:42.354
- FINNI Chewie!
-(BB-8 CHIRPING)

764
00:51:42.474 --> 00:51:44.192
You hurt Chewie.
you're gonna deal with me!

765
00:51:44.310 --> 00:51:46.654
Hurt him? He almost killed me six times!

766
00:51:47.563 --> 00:51:49.031
(CHOKING) Which is fine!

767
00:51:49.148 --> 00:51:50.616
This hyperdrive blows.
there are gonna be...

768
00:51:50.691 --> 00:51:52.659
pieces of us in three different systems.

769
00:51:52.776 --> 00:51:54.619
(HYPERDRIVE NORMALIZING)

770
00:51:56.030 --> 00:51:57.031
What'd you do?

771
00:51:58.073 --> 00:51:59.996
I bypassed the compressor.

772
00:52:02.328 --> 00:52:03.329
Huh.

773
00:52:06.582 --> 00:52:07.879
Move. ball.

774
00:52:08.667 --> 00:52:09.884
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

775
00:52:10.044 --> 00:52:12.138
Ah. don't say that.

776
00:52:12.212 --> 00:52:13.885
You did great. Just rest.

777
00:52:14.798 --> 00:52:15.890
Good job. kid.

778
00:52:16.342 --> 00:52:17.343
Thanks.

779
00:52:17.885 --> 00:52:19.182
- You're welcome.
-(DEVICE HUMS)

780
00:52:19.261 --> 00:52:20.854
(HOLOGRAMS CHITTERING)

781
00:52:23.932 --> 00:52:25.354
HAN; So...

782
00:52:25.476 --> 00:52:26.819
fugitives. huh?

783
00:52:28.729 --> 00:52:30.026
REY: The First Order wants the map.

784
00:52:30.105 --> 00:52:31.402
Finn is with the Resistance.

785
00:52:32.024 --> 00:52:33.446
I'm just a scavenger.

786
00:52:35.486 --> 00:52:36.487
Let's see what you got.

787
00:52:37.363 --> 00:52:39.457
-(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)
- Go ahead.

788
00:52:48.582 --> 00:52:50.755
-(CHEWIE EXCLAIMS)
- HAN: This map's not complete.

789
00:52:50.834 --> 00:52:52.336
It's just a piece.

790
00:52:53.545 --> 00:52:55.343
Ever since Luke disappeared...

791
00:52:55.464 --> 00:52:57.466
people have been looking for him.

792
00:52:57.549 --> 00:52:59.051
REY: Why did he leave?

793
00:53:00.260 --> 00:53:03.013
He was training
a new generation of Jedi.

794
00:53:03.097 --> 00:53:04.770
One boy. an apprentice...

795
00:53:04.848 --> 00:53:07.146
turned against him. destroyed it all.

796
00:53:08.727 --> 00:53:10.650
Luke felt responsible.

797
00:53:10.729 --> 00:53:13.232
He just walked away from everything.

798
00:53:13.941 --> 00:53:15.409
Do you know what happened to him?

799
00:53:15.567 --> 00:53:17.945
A lot of rumors. Stories.

800
00:53:19.947 --> 00:53:22.166
People that knew him best...

801
00:53:23.659 --> 00:53:26.037
think he went looking
for the first Jedi temple.

802
00:53:27.788 --> 00:53:29.131
The Jedi were real?

803
00:53:29.206 --> 00:53:31.425
I used to wonder about that myself.

804
00:53:31.500 --> 00:53:33.719
Thought it was a bunch
of mumbo-jumbo.

805
00:53:34.586 --> 00:53:37.180
A magical power holding
together good and evil...

806
00:53:37.256 --> 00:53:39.384
the dark side and the light.

807
00:53:40.759 --> 00:53:42.932
Crazy thing is...

808
00:53:45.723 --> 00:53:46.770
it's true.

809
00:53:49.309 --> 00:53:50.936
The Force. The Jedi.

810
00:53:53.522 --> 00:53:54.523
All Of it.

811
00:53:57.776 --> 00:53:59.119
It's all true.

812
00:53:59.194 --> 00:54:00.787
(TERMINAL BEEPING)

813
00:54:02.364 --> 00:54:04.492
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)
- No. you rest.

814
00:54:04.616 --> 00:54:07.369
-(CHEWIE GRUMBLES)
- You want my help? You're getting it.

815
00:54:07.453 --> 00:54:09.501
Gonna see an old friend.
She'll get your droid home.

816
00:54:10.789 --> 00:54:12.132
This is our stop.

817
00:54:29.516 --> 00:54:31.018
I didn't know there was
this much green...

818
00:54:31.101 --> 00:54:32.398
in the whole galaxy.

819
00:54:57.252 --> 00:54:58.845
(BIRDS CHIRPING)

820
00:55:00.380 --> 00:55:02.428
Hey. Solo. I'm not sure what
we're walking into here...

821
00:55:02.549 --> 00:55:04.176
Did you just call me Solo?

822
00:55:04.259 --> 00:55:05.886
Sorry. Han. Mr. Solo.

823
00:55:05.969 --> 00:55:07.061
You should know...

824
00:55:07.137 --> 00:55:09.515
I'm a big deal in the Resistance.

825
00:55:09.598 --> 00:55:11.942
Which puts a real target on my back.

826
00:55:12.059 --> 00:55:13.652
Are there any conspirators here?

827
00:55:13.727 --> 00:55:15.604
Like. First Order sympathizers?

828
00:55:15.729 --> 00:55:18.403
Listen. Big Deal.

829
00:55:18.482 --> 00:55:20.405
You got another problem.

830
00:55:20.484 --> 00:55:22.657
Women always figure out the truth.

831
00:55:24.238 --> 00:55:25.581
Always.

832
00:55:31.578 --> 00:55:32.955
You might need this.

833
00:55:34.248 --> 00:55:35.921
I think I can handle myself.

834
00:55:36.041 --> 00:55:38.169
I know you do. That's why
I'm giving it to you.

835
00:55:38.252 --> 00:55:39.253
Take it.

836
00:55:42.089 --> 00:55:43.261
You know how to use one of those?

837
00:55:43.340 --> 00:55:45.013
Yeah. You pull the trigger.

838
00:55:45.092 --> 00:55:46.935
Little bit more to it than that.

839
00:55:47.427 --> 00:55:49.100
You got a lot to learn.

840
00:55:50.514 --> 00:55:51.766
You got a name?

841
00:55:52.683 --> 00:55:53.684
<i>REY -</i>

842
00:55:54.393 --> 00:55:55.394
<i>REY -</i>

843
00:55:59.273 --> 00:56:01.696
I been thinking about bringing
on some more crew. Rey.

844
00:56:01.775 --> 00:56:03.743
A second mate. Someone to help out.

845
00:56:03.819 --> 00:56:05.446
Someone who can keep up
with Chewie and me...

846
00:56:05.529 --> 00:56:07.122
appreciates the Falcon.

847
00:56:07.239 --> 00:56:09.037
Are you offering me a job?

848
00:56:09.116 --> 00:56:11.619
I wouldn't be nice to you.
Doesn't pay much.

849
00:56:11.743 --> 00:56:13.586
You're offering me a job.

850
00:56:14.788 --> 00:56:16.290
I'm thinking about it.

851
00:56:19.960 --> 00:56:21.132
Well?

852
00:56:25.632 --> 00:56:28.306
If you were. I'd be flattered.
But I have to get home.

853
00:56:29.219 --> 00:56:30.721
Where. Jakku?

854
00:56:31.305 --> 00:56:33.103
I've already been away too long.

855
00:56:34.808 --> 00:56:37.186
Chewie. check out the ship
as best you can.

856
00:56:37.311 --> 00:56:38.528
(CH EWIE GRU NTS)

857
00:56:40.898 --> 00:56:43.822
That's too bad. Chewie kind of likes you.

858
00:56:46.904 --> 00:56:48.577
FINN: Solo. why are we here again?

859
00:56:48.697 --> 00:56:50.199
HAN: To get your droid on a clean ship.

860
00:56:50.324 --> 00:56:51.291
REY: Clean?

861
00:56:51.366 --> 00:56:54.245
HAN: You think it was luck
that Chewie and I found the Falcon?

862
00:56:54.912 --> 00:56:56.459
If we can find it on our scanners...

863
00:56:56.538 --> 00:56:58.882
the First Order's not far behind.

864
00:56:58.999 --> 00:57:01.798
Wanna get BB-8 to the Resistance?

865
00:57:01.877 --> 00:57:03.720
Maz Kanata's our best bet.

866
00:57:04.588 --> 00:57:06.090
FINN: We can trust her. right?

867
00:57:06.173 --> 00:57:07.720
HAN: Relax. kid.

868
00:57:07.841 --> 00:57:10.515
She's run this watering hole
for a thousand years.

869
00:57:11.261 --> 00:57:13.309
Maz is a bit of an acquired taste...

870
00:57:13.388 --> 00:57:14.765
so let me do the talking.

871
00:57:14.848 --> 00:57:16.600
And whatever you do. don't stare.

872
00:57:16.683 --> 00:57:17.730
BOTH: At what?

873
00:57:18.769 --> 00:57:19.861
Any of it.

874
00:57:22.272 --> 00:57:24.274
(MELLOW MUSIC PLAYING)

875
00:57:26.902 --> 00:57:29.371
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

876
00:57:41.041 --> 00:57:43.043
- Han Solo!
-(MUSIC STOPS)

877
00:57:43.210 --> 00:57:45.178
-(G LASS SHATTERS)
-(CHATTER CEASES)

878
00:57:47.214 --> 00:57:48.466
(SOFTLY) Oh. boy.

879
00:57:48.590 --> 00:57:49.762
Hey. Maz.

880
00:57:50.592 --> 00:57:51.889
(MUSIC AND CHATTER RESUME)

881
00:57:53.595 --> 00:57:55.563
Where's my boyfriend?

882
00:57:56.056 --> 00:57:57.683
Chewie's working on the Falcon.

883
00:57:57.766 --> 00:57:58.767
I like that Wookiee.

884
00:57:59.559 --> 00:58:01.527
I assume you need something.

885
00:58:01.603 --> 00:58:03.025
Desperately.

886
00:58:03.105 --> 00:58:04.106
Let's get to it.

887
00:58:08.819 --> 00:58:10.446
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

888
00:58:12.572 --> 00:58:14.540
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

889
00:58:14.616 --> 00:58:15.617
(GRUNTS)

890
00:58:19.413 --> 00:58:21.086
(LAUGHING)

891
00:58:21.206 --> 00:58:23.334
(ALL CHITTERING)

892
00:58:23.417 --> 00:58:25.260
(CREATURE EXCLAIMS)

893
00:58:29.423 --> 00:58:31.300
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

894
00:58:39.433 --> 00:58:41.185
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

895
00:58:58.660 --> 00:59:00.128
<i>KYLO REN". Forgive me.</i>

896
00:59:02.789 --> 00:59:04.462
<i>I feel it again.</i>

897
00:59:08.128 --> 00:59:09.675
<i>The pull to the light.</i>

898
00:59:12.507 --> 00:59:15.010
<i>Supreme Leader senses it.</i>

899
00:59:16.094 --> 00:59:17.471
<i>Show me again.</i>

900
00:59:17.971 --> 00:59:20.144
<i>The power of the darkness.</i>

901
00:59:21.433 --> 00:59:24.027
<i>And I will let nothing stand in our way.</i>

902
00:59:24.978 --> 00:59:26.355
<i>Show me...</i>

903
00:59:28.523 --> 00:59:29.866
Grandfather...

904
00:59:32.319 --> 00:59:34.663
<i>and I Will finish...</i>

905
00:59:34.780 --> 00:59:36.157
<i>what you started.</i>

906
00:59:48.960 --> 00:59:50.382
-(BB-8 CHIRPS)
- MAZ: A map.

907
00:59:51.004 --> 00:59:53.132
To Skywalker himself?

908
00:59:53.215 --> 00:59:55.968
(CHUCKLES) You are right back
in the mess.

909
00:59:56.051 --> 00:59:59.521
Maz. I need you to get this droid to Leia.

910
01:00:00.347 --> 01:00:01.348
Hmm...

911
01:00:01.473 --> 01:00:02.474
No.

912
01:00:03.850 --> 01:00:07.855
You've been running away
from this fight for too long.

913
01:00:08.355 --> 01:00:09.322
Han.

914
01:00:09.397 --> 01:00:11.525
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

915
01:00:12.025 --> 01:00:13.527
Go home.

916
01:00:14.194 --> 01:00:15.491
Leia doesn't wanna see me.

917
01:00:15.570 --> 01:00:17.789
Please. we came here for your help.

918
01:00:19.032 --> 01:00:20.033
What fight?

919
01:00:21.243 --> 01:00:23.291
The only fight.

920
01:00:23.370 --> 01:00:25.543
Against the dark side.

921
01:00:25.622 --> 01:00:26.965
Through the ages...

922
01:00:27.040 --> 01:00:29.168
I've seen evil take many forms.

923
01:00:30.252 --> 01:00:32.471
The Sith. The Empire.

924
01:00:32.546 --> 01:00:35.891
Today. it is the First Order.

925
01:00:36.675 --> 01:00:39.599
Their shadow is spreading
across the galaxy.

926
01:00:39.719 --> 01:00:41.096
We must face them.

927
01:00:41.221 --> 01:00:43.269
Fight them.

928
01:00:43.390 --> 01:00:44.937
All of us.

929
01:00:45.559 --> 01:00:47.152
There is no fight against the First Order.

930
01:00:47.227 --> 01:00:48.353
Not one we can win.

931
01:00:49.563 --> 01:00:50.815
Look around.

932
01:00:50.897 --> 01:00:53.275
There's no chance we haven't
been recognized already.

933
01:00:53.400 --> 01:00:55.619
I bet you the First Order
is on their way right...

934
01:00:55.735 --> 01:00:56.782
(GEARS CLICKING)

935
01:00:56.903 --> 01:00:57.904
What's this?

936
01:00:59.739 --> 01:01:00.740
What are you doing?

937
01:01:01.408 --> 01:01:03.752
-(OBJECTS CLATTERING)
-(BB-8 CHIRPS)

938
01:01:05.453 --> 01:01:06.955
Solo. what is she doing?

939
01:01:07.080 --> 01:01:08.832
I don't know. But it ain't good.

940
01:01:08.999 --> 01:01:10.797
If you live long enough...

941
01:01:10.876 --> 01:01:14.380
you see the same eyes
in different people.

942
01:01:15.297 --> 01:01:19.768
I'm looking at the eyes
of a man who wants to run.

943
01:01:22.637 --> 01:01:24.605
You don't know a thing about me.

944
01:01:25.932 --> 01:01:28.936
Where I'm from. What I've seen.

945
01:01:29.603 --> 01:01:32.277
You don't know the First Order like I do.

946
01:01:33.231 --> 01:01:35.404
They'll slaughter us.

947
01:01:35.483 --> 01:01:37.611
We all need to run.

948
01:01:38.737 --> 01:01:39.784
Hmm.

949
01:01:43.950 --> 01:01:45.122
(GRUNTS)

950
01:01:46.077 --> 01:01:47.078
You see those two?

951
01:01:47.787 --> 01:01:49.414
They'll trade work for transportation...

952
01:01:49.539 --> 01:01:50.961
to the Outer Rim.

953
01:01:51.041 --> 01:01:53.260
There. you can disappear.

954
01:01:53.460 --> 01:01:54.461
REY: Finn?

955
01:01:56.880 --> 01:01:57.881
Come with me.

956
01:01:58.924 --> 01:02:00.972
What about BB-8? We're not done yet.

957
01:02:01.051 --> 01:02:02.724
We have to get him back to your base.

958
01:02:03.261 --> 01:02:05.104
(BB-8 CHIRPS ANXIOUSLY)

959
01:02:07.807 --> 01:02:09.150
I can't.

960
01:02:17.943 --> 01:02:19.160
Keep it. kid.

961
01:02:29.412 --> 01:02:30.834
Who's the girl?

962
01:02:31.581 --> 01:02:35.336
(MERCENARIES CONVERSING
IN ALIEN DIALECT)

963
01:02:35.794 --> 01:02:37.762
I was told you can get me
to the Outer Rim.

964
01:02:37.837 --> 01:02:38.929
What are you doing?

965
01:02:40.674 --> 01:02:41.675
Don't leave without me.

966
01:02:42.259 --> 01:02:43.602
(MERCENARY GRUNTS)

967
01:02:45.512 --> 01:02:47.355
You can't just go. I won't let you.

968
01:02:47.430 --> 01:02:48.522
I'm not who you think I am.

969
01:02:48.598 --> 01:02:49.690
Finn. what are you talking about?

970
01:02:49.766 --> 01:02:50.813
I'm not Resistance.

971
01:02:51.518 --> 01:02:53.020
I'm not a hero.

972
01:02:56.273 --> 01:02:58.025
I'm a stormtrooper.

973
01:02:59.192 --> 01:03:02.116
Like all of them. I was taken
from a family I'll never know.

974
01:03:02.862 --> 01:03:04.864
And raised to do one thing.

975
01:03:05.573 --> 01:03:08.702
But my first battle. I made a choice.

976
01:03:09.869 --> 01:03:11.712
I wasn't gonna kill for them.

977
01:03:12.372 --> 01:03:15.296
So I ran. Right into you.

978
01:03:16.876 --> 01:03:18.970
And you looked at me
like no one ever had.

979
01:03:21.881 --> 01:03:24.179
I was ashamed of what I was.

980
01:03:26.720 --> 01:03:28.722
But I'm done with the First Order.

981
01:03:28.847 --> 01:03:30.645
I'm never going back.

982
01:03:32.726 --> 01:03:34.478
Rey. come with me.

983
01:03:35.562 --> 01:03:36.814
Don't go.

984
01:03:41.985 --> 01:03:43.737
Take care of yourself.

985
01:03:45.530 --> 01:03:47.203
Please.

986
01:03:52.746 --> 01:03:55.124
(MERCENARY SPEAKING
ALIEN DIALECT)

987
01:03:58.168 --> 01:03:59.169
(MERCENARY GRUNTS)

988
01:04:00.920 --> 01:04:03.014
YOUNG REY: (FAINTLY) No!

989
01:04:03.089 --> 01:04:05.262
<i>No!</i>

990
01:04:18.563 --> 01:04:21.442
<i>(INDISTINCT) No! Come back!</i>

991
01:04:22.442 --> 01:04:24.240
<i>No!</i>

992
01:04:40.293 --> 01:04:42.136
<i>Come back!</i>

993
01:04:52.472 --> 01:04:54.315
(INDISTINCT) No!

994
01:04:55.642 --> 01:04:56.814
(AIRLOCK CLAN KING)

995
01:05:01.481 --> 01:05:02.858
(BB-8 CHIRPS UNCERTAINLY)

996
01:05:20.667 --> 01:05:22.419
(HINGE CREAKING)

997
01:05:41.312 --> 01:05:42.404
(YELPS)

998
01:05:45.275 --> 01:05:47.118
YOUNG REY: (ECHOING) No!

999
01:05:47.193 --> 01:05:48.740
YODA: (ECHOING) Its energy...

1000
01:05:52.532 --> 01:05:54.580
<i>YODA: ...surrounds us...
MAN: (ECHOING) No!</i>

1001
01:05:54.701 --> 01:05:57.045
YODA: ...and <i>binds</i> us...

1002
01:06:01.583 --> 01:06:02.584
(MAN SCREAMS)

1003
01:06:04.878 --> 01:06:06.004
OBI-WAN: The <i>Force will</i> be...

1004
01:06:06.087 --> 01:06:08.055
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

1005
01:06:15.054 --> 01:06:16.556
YOUNG REY: (ECHOING) No!

1006
01:06:16.681 --> 01:06:18.558
Come back!

1007
01:06:18.683 --> 01:06:20.185
<i>UNKAR". Quiet. girl.</i>

1008
01:06:21.060 --> 01:06:22.061
No!

1009
01:06:26.649 --> 01:06:27.650
OBI-WAN: <i>Rey?</i>

1010
01:06:29.444 --> 01:06:30.616
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1011
01:06:32.238 --> 01:06:34.957
<i>DEA-WAN: These are your first steps.</i>

1012
01:06:39.913 --> 01:06:40.914
What was that?

1013
01:06:43.166 --> 01:06:44.884
I shouldn't have gone in there.

1014
01:06:47.128 --> 01:06:49.597
That lightsaber was Luke's.

1015
01:06:49.672 --> 01:06:51.470
And his father's before him.

1016
01:06:51.591 --> 01:06:55.221
And now. it calls to you.

1017
01:06:55.345 --> 01:06:56.767
I have to get back to Jakku.

1018
01:06:57.430 --> 01:06:59.103
Han told me.

1019
01:07:06.856 --> 01:07:08.904
Dear child.

1020
01:07:08.983 --> 01:07:11.031
I see your eyes.

1021
01:07:11.110 --> 01:07:14.114
You already know the truth.

1022
01:07:14.197 --> 01:07:16.666
Whomever you're waiting for on Jakku...

1023
01:07:17.951 --> 01:07:19.953
they're never coming back.

1024
01:07:26.000 --> 01:07:27.126
But...

1025
01:07:27.210 --> 01:07:29.633
there's someone who still could.

1026
01:07:32.340 --> 01:07:33.933
(SOFTLY) Luke.

1027
01:07:34.008 --> 01:07:37.683
The belonging you seek
is not behind you...

1028
01:07:37.804 --> 01:07:39.477
it is ahead.

1029
01:07:39.597 --> 01:07:43.147
I am no Jedi. but I know the Force.

1030
01:07:43.268 --> 01:07:47.364
It moves through and surrounds
every living thing.

1031
01:07:49.274 --> 01:07:50.867
Close your eyes.

1032
01:07:53.152 --> 01:07:54.153
Feel it.

1033
01:07:55.446 --> 01:07:57.540
The light...

1034
01:07:57.657 --> 01:08:00.035
it's always been there.

1035
01:08:00.159 --> 01:08:02.161
It will guide you.

1036
01:08:04.289 --> 01:08:06.337
The saber. Take it.

1037
01:08:10.336 --> 01:08:12.304
I'm never touching that thing again.

1038
01:08:12.380 --> 01:08:13.882
I don't want any part of this.

1039
01:08:14.007 --> 01:08:15.224
(MAZ STAMMERS)

1040
01:08:17.343 --> 01:08:18.344
Hmm.

1041
01:08:19.345 --> 01:08:20.767
(REY PANTING)

1042
01:08:40.366 --> 01:08:43.870
HUX: <i>(ON</i> PA) <i>Today is the end
of the Republic.</i>

1043
01:08:45.872 --> 01:08:51.379
<i>The end of a regime
that acquiesces to disorder.</i>

1044
01:08:52.670 --> 01:08:56.766
<i>At this very moment.
in a system far from here...</i>

1045
01:08:56.883 --> 01:09:01.730
<i>the New Republic lies to the galaxy...</i>

1046
01:09:01.846 --> 01:09:05.441
<i>while secretly supporting
the treachery...</i>

1047
01:09:06.225 --> 01:09:09.570
<i>of the loathsome Resistance.</i>

1048
01:09:09.646 --> 01:09:13.150
<i>This fierce machine
which you have built...</i>

1049
01:09:13.232 --> 01:09:15.075
<i>upon which we stand...</i>

1050
01:09:15.193 --> 01:09:17.571
<i>will bring an end to the Senate!</i>

1051
01:09:17.654 --> 01:09:20.498
<i>To their cherished fleet!</i>

1052
01:09:20.573 --> 01:09:25.044
<i>All remaining systems
will bow to the First Order!</i>

1053
01:09:25.119 --> 01:09:27.622
<i>And will remember this...</i>

1054
01:09:27.747 --> 01:09:32.799
<i>as the last day of the Republic!</i>

1055
01:09:34.587 --> 01:09:36.715
Confirm transfer to manual control.

1056
01:09:36.798 --> 01:09:38.345
OFFICER: Configure!

1057
01:09:38.466 --> 01:09:39.934
H UX: <i>Fire!</i>

1058
01:09:42.804 --> 01:09:44.056
(ENERGY BUILDING)

1059
01:09:44.180 --> 01:09:45.648
(LOW BOOMING)

1060
01:10:17.964 --> 01:10:19.807
(INDISTINCT SCREAMING)

1061
01:10:31.936 --> 01:10:33.153
(FAINT BOOMING)

1062
01:10:33.813 --> 01:10:35.861
-(FAINT BOOMING)
-(CITIZENS EXCLAIMING)

1063
01:10:37.150 --> 01:10:39.278
(ALL CLAMORING)

1064
01:10:39.986 --> 01:10:42.660
CITIZEN; No. What is it?

1065
01:10:42.822 --> 01:10:44.495
(ALL SCREAMING)

1066
01:10:47.994 --> 01:10:49.917
(CRUMPLING EXPLOSIONS)

1067
01:10:58.671 --> 01:10:59.843
FINN: It was the Republic.

1068
01:11:01.007 --> 01:11:02.634
The First Order. they've done it.

1069
01:11:05.011 --> 01:11:06.183
Where's Rey?

1070
01:11:07.388 --> 01:11:08.605
(REY PANTING)

1071
01:11:21.194 --> 01:11:23.367
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

1072
01:11:23.446 --> 01:11:25.699
- What are you doing?
-(BB-8 CHIRPS)

1073
01:11:26.699 --> 01:11:28.918
- You have to go back.
-(CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

1074
01:11:28.993 --> 01:11:30.119
I'm leaving.

1075
01:11:30.870 --> 01:11:32.372
- BB-8...
-(CHIRPS)

1076
01:11:32.455 --> 01:11:33.547
No. you can't.

1077
01:11:33.623 --> 01:11:35.796
You have to go back.
you're too important.

1078
01:11:35.875 --> 01:11:37.047
They'll help you.

1079
01:11:37.251 --> 01:11:38.468
(ION ENGINES ROARING)

1080
01:11:51.724 --> 01:11:53.021
I've had this for ages.

1081
01:11:57.063 --> 01:11:58.406
Kept it locked away.

1082
01:11:58.856 --> 01:11:59.857
Where'd you get that?

1083
01:12:01.150 --> 01:12:04.245
A good question. For another time.

1084
01:12:05.238 --> 01:12:06.330
Take it.

1085
01:12:06.405 --> 01:12:07.907
Find your friend!

1086
01:12:12.328 --> 01:12:14.205
-(LOW RUMBLING)
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1087
01:12:15.081 --> 01:12:17.083
Those beasts.

1088
01:12:17.208 --> 01:12:18.209
They're here.

1089
01:12:18.334 --> 01:12:19.756
(REY PANTING)

1090
01:12:24.924 --> 01:12:26.426
(LASERS FIRING)

1091
01:12:42.108 --> 01:12:44.782
<i>ST ORMTRQOPER:
FN-417. hold position.</i>

1092
01:12:46.612 --> 01:12:48.285
-(BLASTER CLICKS)
- Oh. safety.

1093
01:12:55.621 --> 01:12:56.622
(BB-8 CHIRPS LOUDLY)

1094
01:13:00.877 --> 01:13:02.049
(REY YELPS)

1095
01:13:13.973 --> 01:13:15.065
STORMTROOPERI Sir.

1096
01:13:15.141 --> 01:13:16.484
<i>The droid was spotted heading west.</i>

1097
01:13:16.559 --> 01:13:17.560
<i>With a girl.</i>

1098
01:13:23.107 --> 01:13:25.576
You have to keep going.
Stay out of sight.

1099
01:13:25.651 --> 01:13:28.495
- I'll try to fight them off.
-(BB-8 CHIRPS NERVOUSLY)

1100
01:13:28.571 --> 01:13:29.823
I hope so. too.

1101
01:13:32.491 --> 01:13:34.493
-(CREATURE GROANS)
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1102
01:13:42.251 --> 01:13:44.174
- Come on. Chewie!
-(CHEWIE GRUNTS)

1103
01:13:46.589 --> 01:13:48.591
MAZ: Rey and BB-8! They need you!

1104
01:13:48.674 --> 01:13:49.675
Now! Go!

1105
01:13:49.759 --> 01:13:52.103
I need a weapon!

1106
01:13:52.178 --> 01:13:53.646
You have one!

1107
01:13:56.349 --> 01:13:57.851
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1108
01:14:03.022 --> 01:14:05.696
- HAN: Hey. can I try that?
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1109
01:14:09.987 --> 01:14:11.330
(STORMTROOPER SCREAMING)

1110
01:14:12.198 --> 01:14:13.666
I like this thing.

1111
01:14:16.327 --> 01:14:17.874
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

1112
01:14:19.622 --> 01:14:20.919
<i>STORMTROOPER: Traitor!</i>

1113
01:14:26.879 --> 01:14:28.677
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

1114
01:14:30.216 --> 01:14:31.718
-(ENERGY CRACKLING)
-(BOTH GRUNTING)

1115
01:15:00.871 --> 01:15:02.544
-(FINN GASPING)
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1116
01:15:05.668 --> 01:15:07.511
- You okay. Big Deal?
- Thanks.

1117
01:15:07.586 --> 01:15:08.587
STORMTROOPER: Don't move-.

1118
01:15:09.839 --> 01:15:11.591
<i>TK-338. we have targets in custody.</i>

1119
01:15:11.757 --> 01:15:12.849
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1120
01:15:14.218 --> 01:15:15.811
(INDISTINCT RADIO CHATTER)

1121
01:15:16.554 --> 01:15:17.680
(ION ENGINES ROARING FAINTLY)

1122
01:15:17.763 --> 01:15:20.016
STORMTROOPER 1:
We have incoming at 28. 6.

1123
01:15:20.099 --> 01:15:22.101
<i>ST ORMTROOP ER 2:
Move! Move! Move!</i>

1124
01:15:23.102 --> 01:15:26.106
<i>Scramble all squads. repeat.
scramble all squads!</i>

1125
01:15:26.188 --> 01:15:27.940
<i>Head to higher cover and wait
for our position!</i>

1126
01:15:28.107 --> 01:15:29.359
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1127
01:15:30.776 --> 01:15:32.278
It's the Resistance.

1128
01:15:40.119 --> 01:15:42.372
Go straight at them!
Don't let these dogs scare you!

1129
01:15:42.455 --> 01:15:44.082
<i>JESS". Copy that.
SNAP: We're with you. Poe.</i>

1130
01:16:12.818 --> 01:16:13.819
HAN: Quick!

1131
01:16:41.806 --> 01:16:44.104
FINN: Whoo! Yeah!

1132
01:16:44.767 --> 01:16:46.610
That's one hell of a pilot!

1133
01:16:46.769 --> 01:16:48.021
Whoo-hoo!

1134
01:16:50.064 --> 01:16:50.940
(REY PANTING)

1135
01:16:55.444 --> 01:16:56.946
(LEAVES RUSTLING)

1136
01:16:57.822 --> 01:16:58.823
(FAINT WHIRRING)

1137
01:17:00.116 --> 01:17:01.368
(INDISTINCT CHITTER)

1138
01:17:02.701 --> 01:17:03.702
<i>mam SABER HUMS)
-(REY GASPS)</i>

1139
01:17:14.171 --> 01:17:15.764
-(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)
-(REY YELPS)

1140
01:17:15.881 --> 01:17:17.098
(BOLTS DEFLECTING)

1141
01:17:30.646 --> 01:17:31.693
(BOLTS DEFLECTING)

1142
01:17:32.189 --> 01:17:33.236
(REY GASPS)

1143
01:17:36.735 --> 01:17:38.282
(REY STRAINING)

1144
01:17:42.366 --> 01:17:44.414
<i>The girl I've heard so much about.</i>

1145
01:17:49.081 --> 01:17:50.583
(REY GASPING)

1146
01:17:56.672 --> 01:17:58.265
<i>The droid.</i>

1147
01:17:59.925 --> 01:18:02.223
-(LIGHTSABER HUMS)
- Where <i>is it?</i>

1148
01:18:07.433 --> 01:18:09.060
<i>ST ORMTROOPER:
Request air support.</i>

1149
01:18:11.395 --> 01:18:12.942
(LOW HUMMING)

1150
01:18:16.192 --> 01:18:17.569
<i>The map.</i>

1151
01:18:19.528 --> 01:18:21.701
<i>You've seen it.</i>

1152
01:18:21.780 --> 01:18:24.124
<i>ST ORMTROOPER:
Sir. Resistance fighters.</i>

1153
01:18:25.075 --> 01:18:26.668
<i>We need more troops.</i>

1154
01:18:26.785 --> 01:18:28.628
<i>KYLO REN'. Pull the division out.</i>

1155
01:18:28.746 --> 01:18:31.795
<i>Forget the droid.
We have what we need.</i>

1156
01:18:38.631 --> 01:18:39.928
<i>ST ORMTROOPER:
Pull back to tree line!</i>

1157
01:18:55.314 --> 01:18:56.861
FINN: No!

1158
01:18:56.941 --> 01:18:58.568
(PANTING)

1159
01:19:00.569 --> 01:19:01.991
No. no!

1160
01:19:03.906 --> 01:19:06.000
No! No!

1161
01:19:07.660 --> 01:19:09.003
Rey!

1162
01:19:28.013 --> 01:19:30.015
FINN: He took her. Did you see that?

1163
01:19:30.849 --> 01:19:32.271
He took her. She's gone.

1164
01:19:32.351 --> 01:19:33.523
Yeah. I know.

1165
01:19:33.644 --> 01:19:34.987
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1166
01:19:42.861 --> 01:19:44.204
RESISTANCE COMMANDER: Let's g0.

1167
01:19:57.876 --> 01:20:00.379
C-3PO: Goodness! Han Solo!

1168
01:20:00.504 --> 01:20:02.677
It is I. C-3PO.

1169
01:20:03.215 --> 01:20:04.717
You probably don't recognize me...

1170
01:20:04.883 --> 01:20:06.351
because of the red arm.

1171
01:20:06.468 --> 01:20:08.391
Look who it is. did you see who...

1172
01:20:08.470 --> 01:20:09.517
(STAMMERS)

1173
01:20:10.180 --> 01:20:11.181
Uh...

1174
01:20:11.724 --> 01:20:12.725
Hmm.

1175
01:20:12.850 --> 01:20:15.899
Excuse me. Prin... General. Sorry.

1176
01:20:15.978 --> 01:20:18.322
- Come along. BB-8. quickly.
-(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

1177
01:20:18.397 --> 01:20:21.071
Yes. I must get
my proper arm reinstalled.

1178
01:20:22.985 --> 01:20:24.737
HAN: You changed your hair.

1179
01:20:27.072 --> 01:20:28.494
LEIA: Same jacket.

1180
01:20:29.742 --> 01:20:31.540
HAN: No. new jacket.

1181
01:20:33.287 --> 01:20:34.789
(CH EWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

1182
01:20:36.498 --> 01:20:38.216
(CHEWIE CHATTERING)

1183
01:20:44.506 --> 01:20:45.507
I saw him.

1184
01:20:47.426 --> 01:20:49.599
Leia. I saw our son.

1185
01:20:51.263 --> 01:20:52.560
He was here.

1186
01:21:13.118 --> 01:21:14.665
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

1187
01:21:26.590 --> 01:21:28.308
(INDISTINCT CHATTER ON PA)

1188
01:21:33.347 --> 01:21:34.348
CREWMANI Hey!

1189
01:21:36.141 --> 01:21:37.142
(BB-8 CHIRPS HAPPILY)

1190
01:21:38.936 --> 01:21:40.813
BB-8. my buddy.

1191
01:21:40.938 --> 01:21:42.906
- Oh. it's so good to see you.
-(BB-8 CHIRPING)

1192
01:21:42.981 --> 01:21:43.982
Finn saved you?

1193
01:21:44.066 --> 01:21:45.158
- Where is he?
-(CHIRPS)

1194
01:21:45.275 --> 01:21:46.492
Poe?

1195
01:21:48.028 --> 01:21:49.029
(LAUGHING) Oh. n0.

1196
01:21:49.530 --> 01:21:51.077
Poe Dameron. you're alive?

1197
01:21:51.156 --> 01:21:53.329
- Buddy! So are you!
- What happened to you?

1198
01:21:53.409 --> 01:21:54.752
I got thrown from the crash.

1199
01:21:54.827 --> 01:21:56.750
I woke up at night.
No you. No ship. Nothing.

1200
01:21:56.829 --> 01:21:58.206
BB-8 says that you saved him.

1201
01:21:58.330 --> 01:21:59.832
No. no. no. It wasn'tjust me.

1202
01:21:59.957 --> 01:22:01.459
You completed my mission. Finn...

1203
01:22:01.542 --> 01:22:02.543
That's my jacket.

1204
01:22:02.709 --> 01:22:05.087
- Oh...
- No. no. no.

1205
01:22:05.170 --> 01:22:06.922
Keep it. It suits you.

1206
01:22:07.798 --> 01:22:09.550
You're a good man. Finn.

1207
01:22:10.467 --> 01:22:12.435
Poe. I need your help.

1208
01:22:13.971 --> 01:22:16.815
ANNOUNCER: <i>(ON PA) PZ-4CO.
report to communications.</i>

1209
01:22:19.893 --> 01:22:20.894
POE: General Organa...

1210
01:22:22.729 --> 01:22:24.857
I'm sorry to interrupt. This is Finn.

1211
01:22:24.982 --> 01:22:27.826
- He needs to talk to you.
- And I need to talk to him.

1212
01:22:27.901 --> 01:22:29.699
That was incredibly brave what you did.

1213
01:22:29.778 --> 01:22:32.372
Renouncing the First Order.
saving this man's life.

1214
01:22:32.489 --> 01:22:34.366
Thank you. ma'am. But a friend
of mine was taken prisoner.

1215
01:22:34.491 --> 01:22:36.368
Han told me about the girl.

1216
01:22:36.452 --> 01:22:37.578
I'm sorry.

1217
01:22:37.703 --> 01:22:39.751
Finn's familiar with the weapon
that destroyed the Hosnian system.

1218
01:22:39.830 --> 01:22:40.831
He worked on the base.

1219
01:22:41.331 --> 01:22:43.254
We're desperate for anything
you can tell us.

1220
01:22:43.375 --> 01:22:44.627
That's where my friend was taken.

1221
01:22:44.710 --> 01:22:46.007
I've got to get there fast.

1222
01:22:46.128 --> 01:22:47.596
And I will do everything I can to help...

1223
01:22:47.671 --> 01:22:49.890
but first you need to tell us
all you know.

1224
01:22:50.048 --> 01:22:51.595
(CHEWIE CHATTERING)

1225
01:22:52.885 --> 01:22:54.603
That sounds very scary.

1226
01:22:54.720 --> 01:22:56.063
(G ROWLS)

1227
01:22:56.722 --> 01:22:58.850
You must be so brave.

1228
01:22:59.016 --> 01:23:00.359
(GRUNTS IN AGREEMENT)

1229
01:23:01.685 --> 01:23:02.686
C-3PO: General...

1230
01:23:02.811 --> 01:23:04.188
I regret to inform you...

1231
01:23:04.271 --> 01:23:05.898
but this map recovered from BB-8...

1232
01:23:05.981 --> 01:23:07.483
is only partially complete.

1233
01:23:07.566 --> 01:23:11.321
And even worse. it matches
no charted system on record.

1234
01:23:11.403 --> 01:23:13.531
We simply do not have
enough information...

1235
01:23:13.614 --> 01:23:15.116
to locate Master Luke.

1236
01:23:16.200 --> 01:23:18.202
Can't believe I was so foolish
to think I could find Luke...

1237
01:23:18.285 --> 01:23:19.286
and bring him home.

1238
01:23:19.411 --> 01:23:20.537
Leia.

1239
01:23:20.621 --> 01:23:21.713
Don't do that.

1240
01:23:21.788 --> 01:23:23.005
Do what?

1241
01:23:23.081 --> 01:23:24.207
Anything-

1242
01:23:25.626 --> 01:23:27.503
C-3PO: Princesses.

1243
01:23:27.628 --> 01:23:29.175
I'm trying to be helpful.

1244
01:23:29.254 --> 01:23:30.255
(CHUCKLES)

1245
01:23:30.339 --> 01:23:31.431
When did that ever help?

1246
01:23:31.507 --> 01:23:33.225
- And don't say the Death Star.
-(HAN SIGHS)

1247
01:23:40.265 --> 01:23:42.233
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

1248
01:23:46.647 --> 01:23:48.365
-(BANGING)
-(CHIRPING)

1249
01:23:48.440 --> 01:23:49.441
C-3POI BB-8.

1250
01:23:49.566 --> 01:23:52.615
- You're wasting your time.
-(CHIRPING)

1251
01:23:52.694 --> 01:23:54.446
It is very doubtful that R2 would have

1252
01:23:54.613 --> 01:23:55.785
the rest of the map in his backup data.

1253
01:23:55.948 --> 01:23:58.076
-(CHIRPING)
- I am afraid not.

1254
01:23:58.158 --> 01:24:02.208
R2-D2 has been in low-power mode
ever since Master Luke went away.

1255
01:24:04.790 --> 01:24:08.044
Sadly. he may never be
his old self again.

1256
01:24:08.627 --> 01:24:09.674
(CHIRPS SADLY)

1257
01:24:09.753 --> 01:24:11.380
HAN: Listen to me. will you?

1258
01:24:12.381 --> 01:24:14.725
I know every time you...

1259
01:24:16.927 --> 01:24:19.305
Every time you look at me
you're reminded of him.

1260
01:24:19.388 --> 01:24:21.390
You think I want to forget him?

1261
01:24:21.473 --> 01:24:23.146
I want him back.

1262
01:24:23.267 --> 01:24:25.361
There's nothing more we could
have done.

1263
01:24:27.104 --> 01:24:28.481
There's too much Vader in him.

1264
01:24:28.564 --> 01:24:31.488
That's why I wanted him
to train with Luke.

1265
01:24:31.567 --> 01:24:33.285
I just never should have sent him away.

1266
01:24:33.360 --> 01:24:34.953
That's when I lost him.

1267
01:24:36.196 --> 01:24:38.198
That's when I lost you both.

1268
01:24:40.284 --> 01:24:42.958
We both had to deal with it
in our own way.

1269
01:24:43.954 --> 01:24:46.924
I went back to the only thing
I was ever any good at.

1270
01:24:47.499 --> 01:24:48.716
We both did.

1271
01:24:50.919 --> 01:24:52.671
We lost our son.

1272
01:24:52.754 --> 01:24:53.926
Forever.

1273
01:24:54.006 --> 01:24:55.007
No.

1274
01:24:55.132 --> 01:24:56.679
It was Snoke.

1275
01:24:57.134 --> 01:24:59.762
He seduced our son to the dark side.

1276
01:24:59.845 --> 01:25:01.438
But we can still save him.

1277
01:25:02.139 --> 01:25:03.265
Me.

1278
01:25:04.182 --> 01:25:05.229
You.

1279
01:25:06.059 --> 01:25:08.403
If Luke couldn't reach him. how could I?

1280
01:25:08.478 --> 01:25:09.900
Luke is a Jedi.

1281
01:25:11.481 --> 01:25:12.824
You're his father.

1282
01:25:15.527 --> 01:25:19.327
There is still light in him. I know it.

1283
01:25:19.406 --> 01:25:21.124
STATURA: General...

1284
01:25:21.199 --> 01:25:23.702
the reconnaissance report
on the enemy base is coming.

1285
01:25:36.340 --> 01:25:37.557
(ION ENGINES ROARING)

1286
01:25:44.473 --> 01:25:46.316
-(METAL CLANGS)
-(REY GASPS)

1287
01:25:50.520 --> 01:25:51.521
Where am I?

1288
01:25:53.857 --> 01:25:55.200
<i>You're my guest.</i>

1289
01:25:55.275 --> 01:25:56.618
Where are the others?

1290
01:25:56.693 --> 01:25:58.366
<i>Do you mean the murderers...</i>

1291
01:25:58.445 --> 01:26:01.324
<i>traitors. and thieves you call friends?</i>

1292
01:26:02.282 --> 01:26:04.751
<i>You'll be relieved to hear
I have no idea.</i>

1293
01:26:06.745 --> 01:26:08.839
<i>You still want to kill me.</i>

1294
01:26:09.623 --> 01:26:11.296
That happens
when you're being hunted...

1295
01:26:11.375 --> 01:26:13.298
by a creature in a mask.

1296
01:26:16.338 --> 01:26:17.635
(HELMET HISSING)

1297
01:26:38.235 --> 01:26:40.078
Tell me about the droid.

1298
01:26:40.904 --> 01:26:42.747
He's a BB unit with a selenium drive...

1299
01:26:42.823 --> 01:26:44.166
and a thermal hyperscan vindicator.

1300
01:26:44.241 --> 01:26:46.369
It's carrying a section
of a navigational chart.

1301
01:26:46.451 --> 01:26:47.828
And we have the rest.

1302
01:26:47.911 --> 01:26:49.709
Recovered from the archives
of the Empire...

1303
01:26:49.788 --> 01:26:50.880
but we need the last piece.

1304
01:26:50.956 --> 01:26:53.425
And somehow you convinced
the droid to show it to you.

1305
01:26:55.043 --> 01:26:56.044
You.

1306
01:26:57.504 --> 01:26:58.756
A scavenger.

1307
01:27:01.091 --> 01:27:03.219
You know I can take whatever I want.

1308
01:27:06.304 --> 01:27:07.601
(REY STRAINING)

1309
01:27:09.349 --> 01:27:11.272
You're so lonely.

1310
01:27:13.270 --> 01:27:14.772
So afraid to leave.

1311
01:27:18.942 --> 01:27:21.866
At night. desperate to sleep.

1312
01:27:24.990 --> 01:27:26.583
You imagine an ocean.

1313
01:27:27.534 --> 01:27:28.831
I see it.

1314
01:27:30.078 --> 01:27:31.830
I see the island.

1315
01:27:36.418 --> 01:27:37.715
And Han Solo.

1316
01:27:40.046 --> 01:27:42.219
You feel like he's the father
you never had.

1317
01:27:42.841 --> 01:27:44.343
He would have disappointed you.

1318
01:27:44.468 --> 01:27:45.765
Get out of my head.

1319
01:27:46.887 --> 01:27:48.434
I know you've seen the map.

1320
01:27:50.015 --> 01:27:51.187
It's in there.

1321
01:27:52.100 --> 01:27:53.352
And now you'll give it to me.

1322
01:27:55.187 --> 01:27:56.359
(REY GRUNTS)

1323
01:27:57.981 --> 01:27:59.073
(STRAINING)

1324
01:28:01.985 --> 01:28:04.033
Don't be afraid. I feel it. too.

1325
01:28:06.490 --> 01:28:08.993
I'm not giving you anything.

1326
01:28:09.618 --> 01:28:10.710
We'll see.

1327
01:28:12.537 --> 01:28:13.629
(LOW HUMMING)

1328
01:28:15.248 --> 01:28:16.875
(STRAINING)

1329
01:28:16.958 --> 01:28:17.959
(GASPS)

1330
01:28:31.473 --> 01:28:33.020
(REY STRAINING)

1331
01:28:50.700 --> 01:28:51.701
You.

1332
01:28:52.786 --> 01:28:53.787
You're afraid.

1333
01:28:56.832 --> 01:28:59.756
That you will never be
as strong as Darth Vader.

1334
01:29:00.627 --> 01:29:01.799
(REY EXHALES)

1335
01:29:01.920 --> 01:29:03.593
(KYLO REN SHUDDERS)

1336
01:29:08.927 --> 01:29:10.770
<i>SNOKE: The scavenger...</i>

1337
01:29:10.887 --> 01:29:12.514
resisted you?

1338
01:29:12.597 --> 01:29:14.190
She is strong with the Force.

1339
01:29:14.266 --> 01:29:16.064
Untrained. but stronger than she knows.

1340
01:29:16.142 --> 01:29:17.359
And the droid?

1341
01:29:17.435 --> 01:29:20.780
Ren believed it was no longer
valuable to us.

1342
01:29:20.856 --> 01:29:23.484
That the girl was all we needed.

1343
01:29:23.608 --> 01:29:26.077
As a result. the droid has
most likely been returned...

1344
01:29:26.152 --> 01:29:27.278
to the hands of the enemy.

1345
01:29:27.404 --> 01:29:29.122
They may have the map already.

1346
01:29:29.197 --> 01:29:30.824
Then the Resistance
must be destroyed...

1347
01:29:30.949 --> 01:29:32.951
before they get to Skywalker.

1348
01:29:33.034 --> 01:29:34.911
HUX: We have their location.

1349
01:29:34.995 --> 01:29:37.623
We tracked their reconnaissance ship
to the lleenium system.

1350
01:29:38.623 --> 01:29:39.920
Good.

1351
01:29:40.000 --> 01:29:42.879
Then we will crush them
once and for all.

1352
01:29:42.961 --> 01:29:44.713
Prepare the weapon.

1353
01:29:45.338 --> 01:29:48.137
Supreme Leader. I can get
the map from the girl.

1354
01:29:48.216 --> 01:29:50.014
I just need your guidance.

1355
01:29:51.636 --> 01:29:55.732
If what you say about this girl is true...

1356
01:29:56.349 --> 01:30:01.025
Bring her to me.

1357
01:30:03.982 --> 01:30:06.030
(INDISTINCT RADIO CHATTER)

1358
01:30:14.993 --> 01:30:17.166
You will remove these restraints...

1359
01:30:17.245 --> 01:30:20.340
and leave this cell with the door open.

1360
01:30:24.085 --> 01:30:25.837
<i>STORMTROOPER". What did you say?</i>

1361
01:30:28.757 --> 01:30:30.259
You will remove these restraints...

1362
01:30:30.342 --> 01:30:33.016
and leave this cell with the door open.

1363
01:30:39.851 --> 01:30:41.398
<i>STORMTROOPER: I'll tighten
those restraints...</i>

1364
01:30:41.519 --> 01:30:43.567
<i>SCHVGHQGF scum.</i>

1365
01:30:57.869 --> 01:30:59.462
You will remove these restraints...

1366
01:30:59.537 --> 01:31:01.915
and leave this cell with the door open.

1367
01:31:05.627 --> 01:31:07.220
<i>STORMTROOPER: I will remove
these restraints...</i>

1368
01:31:07.295 --> 01:31:09.047
<i>and leave the cell with the door open.</i>

1369
01:31:17.973 --> 01:31:21.022
- And you'll drop your weapon.
<i>- And</i> I'll <i>drop my</i> weapon.

1370
01:31:21.101 --> 01:31:22.273
(BLASTER CLATTERS)

1371
01:31:33.738 --> 01:31:34.830
(SOFTLY) No.

1372
01:31:35.824 --> 01:31:36.825
No.

1373
01:31:37.492 --> 01:31:38.664
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1374
01:31:38.743 --> 01:31:39.869
(YELLING) Guards!

1375
01:31:39.953 --> 01:31:41.250
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

1376
01:31:42.414 --> 01:31:43.415
<i>Guards!</i>

1377
01:31:48.420 --> 01:31:50.673
HUX: Begin charging the weapon.

1378
01:31:50.755 --> 01:31:52.098
OFFICER: Yes. sir.

1379
01:31:52.173 --> 01:31:53.470
Weapon charging.

1380
01:31:56.428 --> 01:31:58.101
(ENERGY PULSATING)

1381
01:32:12.736 --> 01:32:14.738
The scan data from Snap's
reconnaissance flight...

1382
01:32:14.821 --> 01:32:16.164
confirms Finn's report.

1383
01:32:16.281 --> 01:32:18.249
They've somehow created
a hyper-lightspeed weapon...

1384
01:32:18.324 --> 01:32:19.621
built within the planet itself.

1385
01:32:19.784 --> 01:32:20.751
A laser cannon?

1386
01:32:20.827 --> 01:32:22.670
We're not sure how to describe
a weapon of this scale.

1387
01:32:22.787 --> 01:32:23.788
EMATT: It's another Death Star.

1388
01:32:23.872 --> 01:32:25.624
I wish that were the case. Major.

1389
01:32:25.707 --> 01:32:26.959
This was the Death Star.

1390
01:32:29.711 --> 01:32:32.214
- And this is Starkiller Base.
-(ALL EXCLAIM)

1391
01:32:32.714 --> 01:32:33.886
So. it's big.

1392
01:32:33.965 --> 01:32:37.060
How is it possible to power
a weapon of that size?

1393
01:32:37.177 --> 01:32:39.305
It uses the power of the sun.

1394
01:32:40.513 --> 01:32:41.685
As the weapon is charged...

1395
01:32:41.806 --> 01:32:43.900
the sun is drained until it disappears.

1396
01:32:43.975 --> 01:32:44.976
AIDE: Ma'am.

1397
01:32:46.978 --> 01:32:48.025
The First Order...

1398
01:32:48.146 --> 01:32:49.568
they're charging the weapon again now.

1399
01:32:50.523 --> 01:32:52.400
Our system is the next target.

1400
01:32:52.525 --> 01:32:53.526
C-3PO: Oh. my.

1401
01:32:53.610 --> 01:32:55.112
Without the Republic fleet.
we're doomed.

1402
01:32:55.195 --> 01:32:56.993
Okay. How do we blow it up?

1403
01:32:57.072 --> 01:32:59.416
- There's always a way to do that.
- Han's right.

1404
01:32:59.491 --> 01:33:01.164
STATURA: In order
for that amount of power...

1405
01:33:01.242 --> 01:33:02.619
to be contained...

1406
01:33:02.702 --> 01:33:04.670
that base has to have some
kind of thermal oscillator.

1407
01:33:04.788 --> 01:33:06.961
There is one. Precinct 47.

1408
01:33:07.540 --> 01:33:08.792
Here.

1409
01:33:08.875 --> 01:33:10.843
STATU RA: If we can destroy
that oscillator...

1410
01:33:10.960 --> 01:33:13.930
it might destabilize the core
and cripple the weapon.

1411
01:33:14.005 --> 01:33:15.803
- Maybe the planet.
- We'll go in there.

1412
01:33:15.882 --> 01:33:17.225
we'll hit that oscillator
with everything we've got.

1413
01:33:17.342 --> 01:33:18.685
They have defensive shields...

1414
01:33:18.760 --> 01:33:20.728
that our ships cannot penetrate.

1415
01:33:20.845 --> 01:33:22.267
We disable the shields.

1416
01:33:22.347 --> 01:33:24.020
Kid. you worked there.

1417
01:33:24.140 --> 01:33:25.141
What do you got?

1418
01:33:25.225 --> 01:33:26.442
I can do it.

1419
01:33:26.518 --> 01:33:27.770
I like this guy.

1420
01:33:27.894 --> 01:33:29.771
I can disable the shields.
but I have to be there.

1421
01:33:29.854 --> 01:33:31.322
On the planet.

1422
01:33:31.397 --> 01:33:33.024
- We'll get you there.
- Han. how?

1423
01:33:33.775 --> 01:33:35.277
If I told you. you wouldn't like it.

1424
01:33:35.401 --> 01:33:37.278
POE: So we disable the shields...

1425
01:33:37.362 --> 01:33:39.660
we take out the oscillator
and we blow up their big gun.

1426
01:33:39.781 --> 01:33:41.875
-(CHEWIE ROARS)
- All right. Let's go.

1427
01:33:42.033 --> 01:33:43.285
(ALL CLAMORING)

1428
01:34:04.389 --> 01:34:05.891
Chewie. check that donal capitator.

1429
01:34:05.974 --> 01:34:07.476
Come on. Let's go.

1430
01:34:07.559 --> 01:34:09.778
Finn. be careful with those.
They're explosives.

1431
01:34:09.894 --> 01:34:10.941
FINN: Now you tell me?

1432
01:34:11.062 --> 01:34:14.282
LEIA: You know. no matter
how much we fought...

1433
01:34:15.692 --> 01:34:18.036
I've always hated watching you leave.

1434
01:34:18.111 --> 01:34:19.328
That's why I did it.

1435
01:34:20.572 --> 01:34:22.074
So you'd miss me.

1436
01:34:24.826 --> 01:34:26.624
I did miss you.

1437
01:34:28.079 --> 01:34:29.877
It wasn't all bad. was it?

1438
01:34:29.956 --> 01:34:31.048
Huh?

1439
01:34:31.124 --> 01:34:34.253
Some of it was... good.

1440
01:34:34.419 --> 01:34:36.092
- Pretty good.
-(HAN CHUCKLES)

1441
01:34:39.424 --> 01:34:42.303
- Some things never change.
- True.

1442
01:34:42.844 --> 01:34:44.846
You still drive me crazy.

1443
01:34:54.022 --> 01:34:55.945
If you see our son...

1444
01:34:58.443 --> 01:35:00.116
bring him home.

1445
01:35:05.533 --> 01:35:08.207
<i>STORMTROOPER: Sir. sensors
triggered in Hangar 718.</i>

1446
01:35:08.286 --> 01:35:09.959
<i>We're searching the area.</i>

1447
01:35:10.038 --> 01:35:12.166
<i>KYLO REN: She's just beginning
to test her powers.</i>

1448
01:35:12.290 --> 01:35:13.963
<i>The longer it takes to find her...</i>

1449
01:35:14.042 --> 01:35:15.715
<i>the more dangerous she becomes.</i>

1450
01:35:20.798 --> 01:35:22.425
ANNOUNCER: (ON PA)
All sentry droids...

1451
01:35:22.508 --> 01:35:23.725
<i>all sentry droids...</i>

1452
01:35:23.801 --> 01:35:26.054
<i>resynchronize
to Galactic Standard Time.</i>

1453
01:35:26.137 --> 01:35:28.139
<i>Offset 473.</i>

1454
01:35:30.892 --> 01:35:31.984
How are we getting in?

1455
01:35:32.101 --> 01:35:34.069
Their shields have
a fractional refresh rate.

1456
01:35:34.145 --> 01:35:35.818
Keeps anything traveling
slower than lightspeed...

1457
01:35:35.980 --> 01:35:37.323
from getting through.

1458
01:35:37.899 --> 01:35:39.993
We're making our landing
approach at lightspeed?

1459
01:35:40.109 --> 01:35:41.326
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1460
01:35:41.444 --> 01:35:42.536
Chewie. get ready.

1461
01:35:43.821 --> 01:35:44.993
And... Now!

1462
01:35:45.114 --> 01:35:46.240
(THRUSTERS FIRING)

1463
01:35:48.910 --> 01:35:50.583
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)
- I am pulling up!

1464
01:35:57.293 --> 01:35:58.920
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)
- I get any higher...

1465
01:35:59.003 --> 01:36:00.255
they'll see us!

1466
01:36:22.193 --> 01:36:24.571
OFFICER: Sir. she was
not found in Hangar 718.

1467
01:36:24.696 --> 01:36:25.788
But all troops are on alert.

1468
01:36:25.863 --> 01:36:27.240
<i>KYLO REN:
Put every hangar on lockdown.</i>

1469
01:36:27.365 --> 01:36:29.038
<i>She's going to try to steal
a ship to esc...</i>

1470
01:36:31.661 --> 01:36:33.208
(SOFTLY) Han Solo.

1471
01:36:44.424 --> 01:36:46.142
The flooding tunnel is over that ridge.

1472
01:36:46.217 --> 01:36:47.469
We'll get in that way.

1473
01:36:47.552 --> 01:36:49.475
What was your job
when you were based here?

1474
01:36:49.554 --> 01:36:50.555
Sanitation.

1475
01:36:53.433 --> 01:36:55.151
- Sanitation?
-(CHEWIE GRUNTS)

1476
01:36:55.226 --> 01:36:56.944
Then how do you know
how to disable the shields?

1477
01:36:57.061 --> 01:36:58.062
I don't.

1478
01:36:58.187 --> 01:36:59.939
I'm just here to get Rey.

1479
01:37:00.064 --> 01:37:03.659
People are counting on us.
The galaxy is counting on us.

1480
01:37:03.735 --> 01:37:05.078
Solo. we'll figure it out.

1481
01:37:06.029 --> 01:37:07.451
We'll use the Force.

1482
01:37:07.572 --> 01:37:09.666
That's not how the Force works.

1483
01:37:09.741 --> 01:37:11.118
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1484
01:37:11.242 --> 01:37:13.791
- Oh. really? You're cold?
-(CHEWIE GRUMBLING)

1485
01:37:13.953 --> 01:37:14.954
FINN: Come on.

1486
01:37:22.378 --> 01:37:23.675
Report.

1487
01:37:23.755 --> 01:37:25.974
Weapon charged in 15 minutes. sir.

1488
01:37:28.426 --> 01:37:29.427
STORMTROOPER: Hey!

1489
01:37:32.597 --> 01:37:34.816
HAN: The longer we're here
the less luck we're gonna have.

1490
01:37:34.932 --> 01:37:37.435
- The shields.
- I have an idea about that.

1491
01:37:43.483 --> 01:37:44.484
(PHASMA GRUNTS)

1492
01:37:45.401 --> 01:37:47.870
- You remember me?
- FN-2187.

1493
01:37:47.945 --> 01:37:49.197
Not anymore.

1494
01:37:49.364 --> 01:37:50.707
The name's Finn and I'm in charge.

1495
01:37:50.782 --> 01:37:52.830
I'm in charge now. Phasma.
I'm in charge.

1496
01:37:52.909 --> 01:37:54.911
- Bring it down. Bring it down.
-(WHISPERS) Yeah.

1497
01:37:54.994 --> 01:37:56.120
Follow me.

1498
01:38:09.300 --> 01:38:10.768
<i>STORMTROOPER 1: Have you
checked out the new T-17s?</i>

1499
01:38:10.843 --> 01:38:12.516
<i>STORMTROOPER 2: The T-17s.
as far as I can tell...</i>

1500
01:38:12.637 --> 01:38:13.684
<i>are a great improvement.</i>

1501
01:38:13.805 --> 01:38:15.648
<i>STORMTROOPER 1". Yeah.
That's what they tell you.</i>

1502
01:38:15.765 --> 01:38:16.982
<i>But believe me. they don't hold up.</i>

1503
01:38:17.100 --> 01:38:18.602
<i>- They don't?
- No.</i>

1504
01:38:20.478 --> 01:38:22.196
-(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)
-(PANTING)

1505
01:38:24.899 --> 01:38:26.116
(INDISTINCT PA CHATTER)

1506
01:38:33.366 --> 01:38:34.788
(FOOTSTEPS RECEDING)

1507
01:38:46.504 --> 01:38:48.302
(STEAM HISSING)

1508
01:38:54.303 --> 01:38:56.055
FINN: You want me to blast
that bucket off your head?

1509
01:38:56.139 --> 01:38:57.265
Lower the shields.

1510
01:38:57.348 --> 01:38:59.191
<i>PHASMA: You're making a big mistake.</i>

1511
01:38:59.308 --> 01:39:01.402
- Do it.
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1512
01:39:02.395 --> 01:39:03.988
(INSTRUMENTS BEEPING)

1513
01:39:05.648 --> 01:39:06.774
Solo. if this works...

1514
01:39:06.858 --> 01:39:09.111
we're not gonna have
a lot of time to find Rey.

1515
01:39:09.193 --> 01:39:10.570
Don't worry. kid.

1516
01:39:11.362 --> 01:39:12.784
We won't leave here without her.

1517
01:39:12.864 --> 01:39:14.457
(INSTRUMENTS BEEPING)

1518
01:39:14.574 --> 01:39:17.453
<i>You can't be so stupid
as to think this will be easy.</i>

1519
01:39:17.535 --> 01:39:20.129
<i>My troops will storm
this block and kill you all.</i>

1520
01:39:20.204 --> 01:39:22.047
I disagree. What do we do with her?

1521
01:39:22.665 --> 01:39:24.212
Is there a garbage chute?

1522
01:39:24.876 --> 01:39:26.219
Trash compactor?

1523
01:39:27.378 --> 01:39:28.470
Yeah. there is.

1524
01:39:28.796 --> 01:39:30.343
General. their shields are down.

1525
01:39:30.423 --> 01:39:32.016
C-3PO: Thank the Maker!

1526
01:39:32.091 --> 01:39:33.843
LEIA: Han did it. Send them in.

1527
01:39:33.926 --> 01:39:35.849
Give Poe full authorization for attack.

1528
01:39:35.928 --> 01:39:38.226
Black Leader.
go to sub-lights on your call.

1529
01:39:38.306 --> 01:39:39.307
Roger. base.

1530
01:39:39.390 --> 01:39:41.108
Red squad. Blue squad. take my lead.

1531
01:39:41.309 --> 01:39:43.311
-(SPEAKING SULLUSTESE)
- Dropping out of lightspeed.

1532
01:39:57.074 --> 01:39:58.576
POE: (ON RADIO) Almost in range.

1533
01:39:58.743 --> 01:40:01.496
Hit the target dead center.
As many runs as we can get.

1534
01:40:01.579 --> 01:40:03.456
- Approaching target.
-(SPEAKING SULLUSTESE)

1535
01:40:07.418 --> 01:40:08.886
OFFICER 1: Fighters incoming!

1536
01:40:09.754 --> 01:40:11.347
OFFICER 2; (ON PA) Coming <i>at 28.336.</i>

1537
01:40:11.422 --> 01:40:13.220
OFFICER 3: Forty-five!
Shields up! Shields up!

1538
01:40:13.299 --> 01:40:14.972
HUX: Dispatch all squadrons.

1539
01:40:15.092 --> 01:40:16.594
Yes. General.

1540
01:40:17.428 --> 01:40:18.429
All right. Let's light it up.

1541
01:40:28.189 --> 01:40:30.283
- Ah. direct hit. (LAUGHS)
- But no damage!

1542
01:40:30.358 --> 01:40:31.610
<i>POE: (ON RADIO) Yeah. we gotta
keep hitting it.</i>

1543
01:40:31.776 --> 01:40:33.073
Another bombing run.

1544
01:40:33.194 --> 01:40:35.913
<i>Remember. when the sun is gone
that weapon will be ready to fire.</i>

1545
01:40:35.988 --> 01:40:38.582
But as long as there's light.
we got a chance.

1546
01:40:39.116 --> 01:40:40.117
(BB-8 CHIRPING RAPIDLY)

1547
01:40:40.284 --> 01:40:41.831
Guys. we got a lot of company!

1548
01:40:48.459 --> 01:40:50.086
<i>STORMTROOPER: We think
they may be splitting up.</i>

1549
01:40:50.169 --> 01:40:52.137
<i>Heading to quadrants 4 and 5.</i>

1550
01:40:59.971 --> 01:41:01.973
We'll use the charges
to blow that blast door.

1551
01:41:02.056 --> 01:41:04.809
I'll go in and draw fire.
but I'm gonna need cover.

1552
01:41:04.892 --> 01:41:05.984
You sure you're up for this?

1553
01:41:06.060 --> 01:41:07.277
Hell. no.

1554
01:41:07.353 --> 01:41:08.650
I'll go in and try to find Rey.

1555
01:41:08.729 --> 01:41:09.946
The troopers will be on our tail.

1556
01:41:10.022 --> 01:41:12.150
We have to be ready for that.

1557
01:41:12.233 --> 01:41:14.031
There's an access tunnel that leads...

1558
01:41:14.110 --> 01:41:16.659
Why are you doing that? Hmm?
Why are you doing this?

1559
01:41:16.737 --> 01:41:18.080
I'm trying to come up with a plan.

1560
01:41:26.831 --> 01:41:28.083
(LAUGHS)

1561
01:41:33.546 --> 01:41:34.718
(ALL YELP)

1562
01:41:34.797 --> 01:41:36.390
HAN: You all right?

1563
01:41:36.465 --> 01:41:38.092
- Yeah.
- Good.

1564
01:41:38.175 --> 01:41:39.768
FINN: What happened to you?
Did he hurt you?

1565
01:41:39.844 --> 01:41:41.221
Finn. what are you doing here?

1566
01:41:41.345 --> 01:41:43.439
- We came back for you.
-(CHEWIE EXCLAIMS)

1567
01:41:44.307 --> 01:41:45.854
What'd he say?

1568
01:41:45.933 --> 01:41:47.310
That it was your idea.

1569
01:41:51.105 --> 01:41:52.197
Thank you.

1570
01:41:56.068 --> 01:41:57.661
How did you get away?

1571
01:41:57.737 --> 01:41:58.784
I can't explain it.

1572
01:41:58.863 --> 01:42:00.957
And you wouldn't believe it.

1573
01:42:01.032 --> 01:42:03.376
Escape now. hug later.

1574
01:42:10.750 --> 01:42:12.218
(ION ENGINES ROARING)

1575
01:42:18.549 --> 01:42:20.096
I got one behind me.

1576
01:42:20.217 --> 01:42:21.594
<i>- You see it?
- Yeah. I'm on it.</i>

1577
01:42:30.227 --> 01:42:32.070
- Burillo's been hit.
- Watch out for ground fire.

1578
01:42:36.984 --> 01:42:38.952
HAN: They're in trouble.

1579
01:42:39.028 --> 01:42:40.450
We can't leave.

1580
01:42:42.239 --> 01:42:45.243
My friend's got a bag full of explosives.

1581
01:42:45.326 --> 01:42:46.999
Let's use them.

1582
01:42:47.078 --> 01:42:48.455
General. are you seeing this?

1583
01:42:48.579 --> 01:42:49.922
RESISTANCE CONTROLLER:
Two more X-wings down.

1584
01:42:49.997 --> 01:42:52.375
That's half our fleet destroyed.

1585
01:42:52.458 --> 01:42:55.132
C-3PO: And their weapon
will be fully charged in ten minutes.

1586
01:42:55.211 --> 01:42:57.339
It would take a miracle to save us now.

1587
01:43:09.100 --> 01:43:10.101
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1588
01:43:18.025 --> 01:43:19.026
(REY GRUNTS)

1589
01:43:23.781 --> 01:43:24.782
HAN: Ah.

1590
01:43:24.865 --> 01:43:27.209
- Girl knows her stuff.
-(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1591
01:43:36.168 --> 01:43:38.637
We'll set the charges
against every other column.

1592
01:43:38.713 --> 01:43:39.760
(G ROWLS)

1593
01:43:39.839 --> 01:43:41.807
You're right. That's a better idea.

1594
01:43:41.882 --> 01:43:43.884
You take the top. I'll go down below.

1595
01:43:43.968 --> 01:43:45.641
- Detonator.
-(CHEWIE GRUNTS)

1596
01:43:45.720 --> 01:43:47.393
We'll meet back here.

1597
01:44:32.808 --> 01:44:33.809
<i>Find them.</i>

1598
01:45:35.579 --> 01:45:36.580
Ben!

1599
01:45:39.458 --> 01:45:40.505
(BLASTER COCKING)

1600
01:45:43.462 --> 01:45:45.135
(G ROWLS)

1601
01:45:49.343 --> 01:45:50.469
Han Solo.

1602
01:45:51.178 --> 01:45:54.057
<i>I've been waiting for this day
for a long time.</i>

1603
01:46:02.940 --> 01:46:03.941
(DOOR OPENING)

1604
01:46:13.325 --> 01:46:16.829
Take off that mask. You don't need it.

1605
01:46:17.413 --> 01:46:19.290
<i>What do you think you'll see if I do?</i>

1606
01:46:19.415 --> 01:46:21.668
The face of my son.

1607
01:46:29.925 --> 01:46:31.518
(HELMET HISSING)

1608
01:46:43.522 --> 01:46:45.695
Your son is gone.

1609
01:46:46.984 --> 01:46:49.328
He was weak and foolish like his father.

1610
01:46:49.486 --> 01:46:51.238
So I destroyed him.

1611
01:46:53.324 --> 01:46:55.702
That's what Snoke wants you to believe.

1612
01:46:56.952 --> 01:46:58.670
But it's not true.

1613
01:46:59.997 --> 01:47:02.091
My son is alive.

1614
01:47:02.166 --> 01:47:03.634
No.

1615
01:47:03.709 --> 01:47:05.928
The Supreme Leader is wise.

1616
01:47:06.003 --> 01:47:08.756
Snoke is using you for your power.

1617
01:47:08.839 --> 01:47:10.637
When he gets what he wants.
he'll crush you.

1618
01:47:15.888 --> 01:47:17.561
You know it's true.

1619
01:47:23.187 --> 01:47:24.188
It's too late.

1620
01:47:24.271 --> 01:47:25.864
No. it's not.

1621
01:47:25.940 --> 01:47:27.692
Leave here with me. Come home.

1622
01:47:29.443 --> 01:47:30.865
We miss you.

1623
01:47:39.578 --> 01:47:41.706
(VOICE BREAKING)
I'm being torn apart.

1624
01:47:44.541 --> 01:47:46.714
I want to be free of this pain.

1625
01:47:52.132 --> 01:47:53.179
I know what I have to do...

1626
01:47:53.258 --> 01:47:55.386
but I don't know if I have
the strength to do it.

1627
01:47:59.306 --> 01:48:00.398
Will you help me?

1628
01:48:00.474 --> 01:48:02.317
Yes. Anything.

1629
01:48:48.689 --> 01:48:49.781
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1630
01:48:50.607 --> 01:48:53.451
-(CHEWIE HOWLING)
- REYI No!

1631
01:48:53.527 --> 01:48:55.404
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

1632
01:49:00.367 --> 01:49:01.619
Thank you.

1633
01:49:09.126 --> 01:49:10.127
No.

1634
01:49:45.537 --> 01:49:46.834
(CHEWIE HOWLS)

1635
01:49:47.873 --> 01:49:48.920
(GROANS)

1636
01:49:50.751 --> 01:49:52.094
(CHEWIE ROARS)

1637
01:50:11.814 --> 01:50:13.441
(CRUMPLING EXPLOSIONS)

1638
01:50:25.452 --> 01:50:27.045
The oscillator's been damaged...

1639
01:50:27.121 --> 01:50:28.873
-but is still functional.
-(ALARMS BEEPING)

1640
01:50:28.956 --> 01:50:31.459
Admiral. their weapon
will fire in two minutes.

1641
01:50:42.719 --> 01:50:44.187
FINN: The Falcon's this way.

1642
01:50:49.059 --> 01:50:50.606
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1643
01:50:52.062 --> 01:50:53.405
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

1644
01:51:05.075 --> 01:51:06.418
We're not done yet.

1645
01:51:09.580 --> 01:51:11.423
You're a monster.

1646
01:51:11.540 --> 01:51:13.417
It's just us now.

1647
01:51:14.585 --> 01:51:16.087
Han Solo can't save you.

1648
01:51:16.920 --> 01:51:18.263
(KYLO REN GRUNTING)

1649
01:51:24.887 --> 01:51:26.685
-(REY SCREAMING)
- FINN: Rey!

1650
01:51:29.474 --> 01:51:30.976
<i>REY -</i>

1651
01:51:31.059 --> 01:51:32.060
Rey!

1652
01:51:33.896 --> 01:51:35.523
Oh. no. No. no.

1653
01:51:35.606 --> 01:51:36.607
<i>REY -</i>

1654
01:51:36.690 --> 01:51:38.192
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

1655
01:51:38.817 --> 01:51:40.364
(YELLING) Traitor!

1656
01:51:47.618 --> 01:51:49.370
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1657
01:51:50.913 --> 01:51:52.460
That lightsaber.

1658
01:51:53.582 --> 01:51:54.629
It belongs to me.

1659
01:51:54.708 --> 01:51:56.381
Come get it.

1660
01:51:56.460 --> 01:51:57.712
(YELLING)

1661
01:51:57.794 --> 01:51:59.637
(LIGHTSABERS CRACKLING)

1662
01:52:05.135 --> 01:52:06.557
(KYLO REN WINCING)

1663
01:52:17.814 --> 01:52:20.067
(ENERGY CRACKLING)

1664
01:52:20.150 --> 01:52:21.652
(FINN GRUNTS)

1665
01:52:25.489 --> 01:52:26.991
-(FINN GASPING)
-(SIZZLING)

1666
01:52:27.074 --> 01:52:28.997
(FINN SCREAMING)

1667
01:52:30.327 --> 01:52:31.670
(SCREAMING CONTINUES)

1668
01:52:35.832 --> 01:52:37.129
(KYLO REN GRUNTS)

1669
01:52:43.590 --> 01:52:44.591
(FINN GROANS)

1670
01:52:47.010 --> 01:52:48.478
(LIGHTSABER DEACTIVATING)

1671
01:52:49.763 --> 01:52:51.185
(FAINT RUMBLING)

1672
01:52:57.187 --> 01:52:58.188
(GRUNTS)

1673
01:53:18.375 --> 01:53:19.547
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1674
01:53:19.626 --> 01:53:21.173
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

1675
01:53:24.631 --> 01:53:25.883
(REY YELLING)

1676
01:53:44.192 --> 01:53:45.284
We just lost R-1.

1677
01:53:45.902 --> 01:53:47.199
<i>JESS: We're overwhelmed.</i>

1678
01:53:47.279 --> 01:53:48.576
What do we do? It isn't working.

1679
01:53:49.323 --> 01:53:51.542
Black Leader. there's a brand
new hole in that oscillator.

1680
01:53:52.576 --> 01:53:54.499
<i>Looks like our friends got in.</i>

1681
01:53:55.120 --> 01:53:56.997
Red Four. Red Six. cover us.

1682
01:53:57.080 --> 01:53:58.252
- I'm on it.
- Roger.

1683
01:53:58.332 --> 01:53:59.879
Everybody else. hit the target hard.

1684
01:53:59.958 --> 01:54:01.005
Give it everything you got.

1685
01:54:13.889 --> 01:54:15.266
I need some help here.
I need some help!

1686
01:54:15.349 --> 01:54:16.601
- Coming in!
- Watch out!

1687
01:54:17.809 --> 01:54:19.061
I'm hit!

1688
01:54:24.566 --> 01:54:26.489
All teams. I'm going in.

1689
01:54:26.610 --> 01:54:27.782
<i>Pull up and cover me.</i>

1690
01:54:27.861 --> 01:54:29.613
Copy that. Black Leader.
Good luck. Poe.

1691
01:54:35.744 --> 01:54:37.621
Weapon fully charged in 30 seconds.

1692
01:54:39.122 --> 01:54:40.294
Prepare to fire.

1693
01:55:10.695 --> 01:55:12.197
(FAINT RUMBLING)

1694
01:55:22.332 --> 01:55:24.334
-(REY GRUNTING)
-(LIGHTSABERS CRACKLING)

1695
01:55:29.840 --> 01:55:31.012
(KYLO REN GRUNTING)

1696
01:55:40.016 --> 01:55:41.859
(LIGHTSABERS HUMMING)

1697
01:55:52.279 --> 01:55:53.531
(RUMBLING)

1698
01:56:00.704 --> 01:56:01.705
(REY GRUNTING)

1699
01:56:02.873 --> 01:56:03.874
(REY YELPS)

1700
01:56:10.046 --> 01:56:11.798
(LIGHTSABERS CRACKLING)

1701
01:56:11.923 --> 01:56:13.300
(REY STRAINING)

1702
01:56:13.383 --> 01:56:14.805
You need a teacher.

1703
01:56:16.678 --> 01:56:18.476
I could show you the ways of the Force.

1704
01:56:21.099 --> 01:56:22.191
(SOFTLY) The Force?

1705
01:56:23.935 --> 01:56:25.733
(BREATHING SLOWS)

1706
01:56:29.357 --> 01:56:30.904
(BREATHING CALMLY)

1707
01:56:52.005 --> 01:56:53.803
-(LIGHTSABER CRACKLES)
-(KYLO REN GRUNTS)

1708
01:56:55.342 --> 01:56:56.343
(GROANS)

1709
01:56:56.426 --> 01:56:57.803
(YELLS)

1710
01:57:13.109 --> 01:57:15.328
-(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)
-(KYLO REN GROANING)

1711
01:57:19.824 --> 01:57:20.825
(REY YELLS)

1712
01:57:21.284 --> 01:57:23.127
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

1713
01:57:24.454 --> 01:57:25.751
(YELLING)

1714
01:57:33.838 --> 01:57:35.010
(KYLO REN SCREAMS)

1715
01:57:41.096 --> 01:57:42.439
(GROANING)

1716
01:57:44.140 --> 01:57:45.392
(DEEP RUMBLING)

1717
01:58:01.199 --> 01:58:02.200
(LIGHTSABER DEACTIVATES)

1718
01:58:05.620 --> 01:58:07.042
(ALARMS BEEPING)

1719
01:58:07.122 --> 01:58:08.874
(OFFICERS CLAMORING)

1720
01:58:10.959 --> 01:58:12.381
OFFICER 1: All eyes on that TIE fighter.

1721
01:58:12.460 --> 01:58:14.053
OFFICER 2: We're losing power rapidly!

1722
01:58:16.423 --> 01:58:18.346
DATOO: Lieutenant!
Get back to your station!

1723
01:58:18.425 --> 01:58:21.725
Just look! We won't survive.
Even Hux is gone.

1724
01:58:21.845 --> 01:58:23.347
HUX: Supreme Leader.

1725
01:58:24.222 --> 01:58:26.190
The fuel cells have ruptured.

1726
01:58:26.266 --> 01:58:28.394
The collapse of the planet has begun.

1727
01:58:28.602 --> 01:58:32.652
Leave the base at once
and come to me with Kylo Ren.

1728
01:58:33.732 --> 01:58:35.609
It is time...

1729
01:58:35.692 --> 01:58:38.036
to complete his training.

1730
01:58:40.363 --> 01:58:41.364
Finn!

1731
01:58:42.115 --> 01:58:43.332
Finn.

1732
01:58:53.627 --> 01:58:55.049
(THRUSTERS HUMMING)

1733
01:59:32.457 --> 01:59:35.552
- All teams. I got eyes on them.
- Yes!

1734
01:59:58.483 --> 02:00:01.612
Our job's done here. Let's go home.

1735
02:00:09.786 --> 02:00:11.413
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

1736
02:00:13.415 --> 02:00:14.632
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1737
02:00:16.793 --> 02:00:19.137
MEDIC: Easy. easy. He's hurt.

1738
02:00:19.254 --> 02:00:20.471
We've got a heartbeat.

1739
02:00:21.423 --> 02:00:22.470
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1740
02:01:06.134 --> 02:01:07.351
(CHEWIE MOANS)

1741
02:01:11.347 --> 02:01:12.519
(R2-D2 BEEPING)

1742
02:01:17.187 --> 02:01:18.188
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

1743
02:01:18.313 --> 02:01:20.031
(CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

1744
02:01:20.148 --> 02:01:21.525
(R2-D2 BEEPING)

1745
02:01:22.525 --> 02:01:24.152
-(BB-8 CHIRPING)
- C-3POI R2-D2!

1746
02:01:25.028 --> 02:01:26.029
You've come back.

1747
02:01:26.988 --> 02:01:28.911
(R2-D2 BEEPING EXCITEDLY)

1748
02:01:29.991 --> 02:01:31.413
- C-3PO: You found what?
-(R2-D2 BEEPS)

1749
02:01:31.534 --> 02:01:33.536
- How dare you call me that!
-(CLANGING)

1750
02:01:34.537 --> 02:01:35.834
(BEEPING RAPIDLY)

1751
02:01:35.914 --> 02:01:38.008
- Find Master Luke. how?
-(BEEPING)

1752
02:01:38.082 --> 02:01:39.129
Come. R2.

1753
02:01:39.209 --> 02:01:41.211
We must go tell the others at once!

1754
02:01:42.545 --> 02:01:43.637
C-3PO: General.

1755
02:01:43.713 --> 02:01:45.886
Excuse me. General.

1756
02:01:46.007 --> 02:01:47.759
(R2-D2 BEEPING)

1757
02:01:50.470 --> 02:01:52.973
R2 may contain some
much-needed good news.

1758
02:01:53.640 --> 02:01:55.108
Tell me.

1759
02:02:03.900 --> 02:02:05.402
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

1760
02:02:05.485 --> 02:02:06.907
Yeah. All right. buddy. Hold on.

1761
02:02:21.334 --> 02:02:22.961
C-3PO: The map. it is complete.

1762
02:02:23.586 --> 02:02:25.259
LEIA: Luke.

1763
02:02:25.338 --> 02:02:26.931
C-3PO: Oh. my dear friend...

1764
02:02:27.048 --> 02:02:28.595
-how I've missed you.
-(R2-D2 BEEPS HAPPILY)

1765
02:02:32.846 --> 02:02:34.018
(RHYTHMIC BEEPING)

1766
02:02:45.567 --> 02:02:47.615
We'll see each other again.

1767
02:02:47.694 --> 02:02:49.617
I believe that.

1768
02:02:57.787 --> 02:02:59.585
Thank you. my friend.

1769
02:03:14.470 --> 02:03:16.313
LEIA: Rey.

1770
02:03:17.974 --> 02:03:20.773
May the Force be with you.

1771
02:03:23.813 --> 02:03:25.065
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

1772
02:03:25.565 --> 02:03:27.567
(CHIRPING INQUISITIVELY)

1773
02:03:44.000 --> 02:03:45.547
(ENGINES FIRING)

1774
02:03:45.668 --> 02:03:47.670
(ALL CHEERING)

1775
02:04:07.857 --> 02:04:09.109
(CH EWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

1776
02:04:45.186 --> 02:04:46.733
(CHEWIE GROWLS FAINTLY)

1777
02:04:48.314 --> 02:04:49.736
(R2-D2 BEEPS FAINTLY)

1778
02:05:09.168 --> 02:05:10.545
(PANTING)

